WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.492
The subject

00:00:02.572 --> 00:00:08.263
that has been placed before you today

00:00:08.925 --> 00:00:13.146
is most fascinating and absorbing:

00:00:16.028 --> 00:00:22.227
Kundalini and Jesus Christ, Lord Jesus Christ. For ordinary,

00:00:22.307 --> 00:00:26.956
common people this is something entirely new,

00:00:27.036 --> 00:00:31.479
and till this day no one has ever drawn any

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:35.898
connection between the two in this manner.

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:43.001
The reason for this

00:00:47.203 --> 00:00:51.673
is that whenever flowers have blossomed

00:00:51.753 --> 00:00:54.503
upon the tree of Dharma,

00:00:54.583 --> 00:01:01.001
they have spread their fragrance through many provinces,

00:01:01.081 --> 00:01:05.093
many countries, and many languages.

00:01:05.173 --> 00:01:10.674
But what relationship they bore to one another —

00:01:10.754 --> 00:01:14.765
that only the tree itself can know.

00:01:16.046 --> 00:01:21.662
Wherever they blossomed, wherever their fragrance spread,

00:01:21.742 --> 00:01:27.358
the people there never truly accepted them. So how, then,

00:01:27.438 --> 00:01:30.985
could others ever know or understand

00:01:31.065 --> 00:01:36.583
that these flowers all bloom upon one and the same tree?

00:01:36.663 --> 00:01:39.028
Now I am speaking to you

00:01:39.108 --> 00:01:40.981
from that direction

00:01:41.061 --> 00:01:42.261
to which you

00:01:43.142 --> 00:01:45.462
have not yet been brought.

00:01:45.542 --> 00:01:52.503
Once you reach there, you will understand My words very easily. For at present

00:01:52.583 --> 00:01:58.831
you have no way of knowing whether what I am saying is true or untrue;

00:01:58.911 --> 00:02:01.320
you possess no proof of it.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:06.220
How will you know whether what I say is true or false?

00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:11.208
The way to know it is this — and the difficulty is that

00:02:11.288 --> 00:02:15.318
you have not yet learned to discover your own meaning.

00:02:15.398 --> 00:02:17.114
You are not yet at that

00:02:17.194 --> 00:02:21.149
level where you have become connected with the Truth.

00:02:21.229 --> 00:02:26.453
For this very reason you cannot tell whether a thing is true or false,

00:02:26.533 --> 00:02:31.085
whether it is mere legend or something fashioned by the mind.

00:02:31.165 --> 00:02:34.448
Those who, as we say, have become realized —

00:02:34.528 --> 00:02:39.528
they can come to know fully which thing is true and which is false.

00:02:39.608 --> 00:02:42.684
Because of the vibrations that flow from their

00:02:42.764 --> 00:02:46.175
hands — the experiment we conducted here yesterday,

00:02:46.255 --> 00:02:48.596
when these vibrations began to flow

00:02:48.676 --> 00:02:50.950
from the hands of so many people —

00:02:51.030 --> 00:02:53.973
if you observe and weigh this carefully, you

00:02:54.053 --> 00:02:58.400
will understand that what I am telling you is the complete Truth.

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.887
Christians know of Jesus Christ only

00:03:00.967 --> 00:03:06.117
through the Bible, which is a most profound book. Its depth is so great that,

00:03:06.197 --> 00:03:08.471
being unable to grasp its meaning,

00:03:08.551 --> 00:03:12.455
these people make all sorts of attempts at interpretation.

00:03:12.535 --> 00:03:15.497
For instance, it is written in the Bible, "I

00:03:15.577 --> 00:03:20.155
will appear before you like tongues of flames." They cannot give the

00:03:20.235 --> 00:03:24.543
meaning of this. They imagine that when God appears before them,

00:03:24.623 --> 00:03:29.335
such flames will come pouring out of Him. But that is not its meaning.

00:03:29.415 --> 00:03:33.992
Its meaning is this: I shall become visible to you in the Sahasrara.

00:03:34.072 --> 00:03:36.563
It is a description of the Sahasrara.

00:03:36.643 --> 00:03:40.597
The Kundalini is described in many ways in the Bible.

00:03:40.677 --> 00:03:43.960
I can give you countless quotations from it.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:48.890
Jesus Christ has said, "Those who are not against Me are with Me"

00:03:48.970 --> 00:03:52.849
— those who are not in opposition to Me are with Me.

00:03:52.929 --> 00:03:58.301
If you go and ask the Christians who these people are, they do not know.

00:03:58.381 --> 00:03:59.948
They have made it out

00:04:02.150 --> 00:04:07.213
that Jesus Christ said, "I am the path, I am the door"

00:04:07.293 --> 00:04:10.387
— I am the way and I am the door.

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:14.592
But He did not say, "I am the destination" —

00:04:14.672 --> 00:04:19.078
He never said that He was the goal. If He said,

00:04:19.158 --> 00:04:24.690
"I am the way and I am the door," then the destination must

00:04:24.770 --> 00:04:30.176
be something beyond. Even after speaking in such profound language,

00:04:30.256 --> 00:04:32.838
the wicked people of that time —

00:04:32.918 --> 00:04:37.276
within four years, they let Him live only four years —

00:04:37.356 --> 00:04:41.310
within four years they nailed Him upon the cross.

00:04:41.390 --> 00:04:44.617
And even today, those who believe in Him

00:04:44.697 --> 00:04:51.395
and say that they follow His religion go on, every single day, sacrificing all that

00:04:51.475 --> 00:04:53.008
He truly stood for.

00:04:53.088 --> 00:05:00.283
As I told you yesterday, the Hindus are just as foolish, and so are the Muslims,

00:05:00.363 --> 00:05:02.701
and so are the Christians.

00:05:03.622 --> 00:05:09.587
About this Jesus Christ — if you could ever read the Devi Bhagavata,

00:05:09.667 --> 00:05:11.772
you would discover there

00:05:11.852 --> 00:05:16.940
that Shri Radha created Him out of Her own inner strength,

00:05:17.020 --> 00:05:19.915
and gave Him the name Mahavishnu.

00:05:19.995 --> 00:05:24.995
She made it in two parts — She formed it as an egg-shape.

00:05:25.075 --> 00:05:28.847
The base of this egg-shape is Shri Ganesha.

00:05:28.927 --> 00:05:32.348
It is Shri Ganesha who is fundamentally

00:05:32.428 --> 00:05:34.216
the power of Jesus Christ.

00:05:34.296 --> 00:05:39.798
And the other part of the egg-shape — the one we call Shadanana, Shanmukhanana —

00:05:39.878 --> 00:05:41.597
that is called Kartikeya.

00:05:41.677 --> 00:05:45.735
The very life-breath within this whole egg is Jesus Christ.

00:05:45.815 --> 00:05:50.560
The complete Brahma tattwa, the Omkara — that itself is Jesus Christ.

00:05:50.640 --> 00:05:55.454
The entire existence of the Kundalini is, one may say, because of Him.

00:05:55.534 --> 00:05:59.729
And it is He who is seated at the very base of the Kundalini.

00:05:59.809 --> 00:06:01.628
Shri Radha gave Him birth.

00:06:01.708 --> 00:06:05.554
You will come to know this if you read the Devi Purana.

00:06:05.634 --> 00:06:10.251
But where are our modern people of today ready to read Markandeya!

00:06:10.331 --> 00:06:15.157
You will not find a seer like Markandeya however much you may search.

00:06:15.237 --> 00:06:18.734
He has described the most subtle, intricate things

00:06:18.814 --> 00:06:22.172
about the Devi — what the marks of the Devi are,

00:06:22.252 --> 00:06:26.728
how the Devi dresses, what the Devi delights in, how She is, Her

00:06:26.808 --> 00:06:29.874
ways and bearing, Her nature. Sometimes one is

00:06:29.954 --> 00:06:33.287
filled with wonder at how he came to know so much.

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:36.745
But our modern people of today,

00:06:36.825 --> 00:06:40.284
educated in English learning, are not even willing

00:06:40.364 --> 00:06:43.546
to accept that there exists in this world such

00:06:43.626 --> 00:06:47.293
a thing as the Devi, or such a thing as divine power.

00:06:47.373 --> 00:06:51.316
Although today the English are turning in this direction,

00:06:51.396 --> 00:06:56.446
our Indians are still being very great Englishmen. I say many times that,

00:06:56.526 --> 00:07:00.124
leaving aside the country of the English themselves,

00:07:00.204 --> 00:07:03.801
there are more Englishmen here in our India. I think

00:07:05.437 --> 00:07:09.728
very few among you would have read the Markandeya Purana.

00:07:09.808 --> 00:07:13.950
But if you read in it the establishment of Mahavishnu —

00:07:14.030 --> 00:07:18.621
if you give your attention to that — you will understand that

00:07:18.701 --> 00:07:23.218
this whole thing is none other than a description of Christ,

00:07:23.298 --> 00:07:24.498
of the Christ.

00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:30.786
Shri Radha created Him by Her own power, which is the power of Mahalakshmi.

00:07:30.866 --> 00:07:34.398
And His mother, who was Mary, was none other than

00:07:34.478 --> 00:07:39.236
— you should simply understand this directly — Shri Radha Herself.

00:07:39.316 --> 00:07:43.641
It was Shri Radha Herself, in person, who gave birth to Him.

00:07:43.721 --> 00:07:46.460
Radha — "Ra" means energy, Shakti; and

00:07:46.540 --> 00:07:49.856
"dha" means the one who holds and sustains it.

00:07:49.936 --> 00:07:55.198
She who held the power within Herself, She is Radha. This Radha is a form

00:07:55.278 --> 00:07:58.617
of Mahalakshmi. Shri Radha incarnated upon this earth.

00:07:58.697 --> 00:08:01.665
She who was earlier Shri Sita became Shri Radha.

00:08:01.745 --> 00:08:05.826
And it was Shri Radha who took Shri Ganesha into Her lap — because

00:08:05.906 --> 00:08:08.689
Shri Radha is the Incarnation of Mahalakshmi,

00:08:08.769 --> 00:08:11.613
and Shri Ganesha had been created by Mahakali,

00:08:11.693 --> 00:08:16.825
in the form of Gauri — She took Him into Her lap, and giving Him this special form,

00:08:16.905 --> 00:08:21.172
She made Him Krishta. Now this word "Krishta" too comes from Krishna,

00:08:21.252 --> 00:08:23.416
because His father is Shri Krishna;

00:08:23.496 --> 00:08:28.965
that is why He was called Krishta. This is something to be understood very deeply.

00:08:29.045 --> 00:08:32.179
And His name Jesus was created in this way too:

00:08:32.259 --> 00:08:36.994
the thought came to Shri Radha that the name Yashoda had never appeared

00:08:37.074 --> 00:08:41.476
anywhere until now. Yashoda — "yash" meaning fame and "de" meaning

00:08:41.556 --> 00:08:44.757
to give, the one who gives fame, and so Yashoda.

00:08:44.837 --> 00:08:47.438
But if we look here in our own country,

00:08:47.518 --> 00:08:50.453
He is called Yeshu and Jeshu, in short form.

00:08:50.533 --> 00:08:52.867
If the name Yashoda is used in U.P.

00:08:52.947 --> 00:08:57.184
and such places, it is shortened to Jasu. That very name, Jasu,

00:08:57.264 --> 00:09:02.307
is what She gave to Him. In this way the name Jesus Christ came into being.

00:09:06.435 --> 00:09:11.663
Now Hindu people feel that Jesus Christ has, after all, become one of our own.

00:09:11.743 --> 00:09:15.430
But are you even Hindu? You are not even really Indian.

00:09:15.510 --> 00:09:19.196
And Hindutva does not mean to quarrel over some thing —

00:09:19.276 --> 00:09:21.153
that is not Hindutva at all.

00:09:21.233 --> 00:09:25.389
Hindutva is understood to belong to the worshippers of Shakti.

00:09:25.469 --> 00:09:28.619
Only those who are flooded with Shakti, who are

00:09:28.699 --> 00:09:32.989
cultured and sanctified by Shakti, are to be regarded as Hindus.

00:09:33.069 --> 00:09:36.085
Those within whom the Shakti has not yet been

00:09:36.165 --> 00:09:38.728
awakened cannot be regarded as Hindus.

00:09:38.808 --> 00:09:44.000
In this way you can understand that Jesus Christ is a very great Incarnation,

00:09:44.080 --> 00:09:45.564
created by Shri Radha,

00:09:45.644 --> 00:09:47.464
from the time of Vaikuntha.

00:09:47.544 --> 00:09:50.983
It is described of Him that Shri Radha created Him.

00:09:51.063 --> 00:09:54.300
Out of that, He was then divided into two parts.

00:09:54.380 --> 00:09:59.033
One part She left just as it was, which was the part of Shri Ganesha.

00:09:59.113 --> 00:10:02.080
And the other part She gave a special form —

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.723
that egg She gave the form of a child.

00:10:04.803 --> 00:10:07.816
Then this child kept weeping for many years.

00:10:07.896 --> 00:10:09.608
He remembered his father.

00:10:09.688 --> 00:10:14.619
When his father saw him — that is, when Krishna, Shri Krishna, saw him —

00:10:14.699 --> 00:10:16.480
He granted him many boons.

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:20.600
One of these boons is this: "You shall sit higher than Me."

00:10:20.680 --> 00:10:23.009
See, our Vishuddhi chakra is here,

00:10:23.089 --> 00:10:25.075
and our Agnya chakra is here.

00:10:25.155 --> 00:10:28.373
But in the brain, the Vishuddhi chakra is here.

00:10:28.453 --> 00:10:32.425
The seat of the Vishuddhi chakra inside the brain is here.

00:10:32.505 --> 00:10:34.423
Yet in terms of the chakras,

00:10:34.503 --> 00:10:37.431
Shri Krishna's chakra is this one, and

00:10:37.511 --> 00:10:40.285
above it, here, is the Agnya chakra,

00:10:40.365 --> 00:10:42.600
where Jesus Christ is seated.

00:10:42.680 --> 00:10:49.153
The second thing He said was: "You shall remain the foundation of the entire world."

00:10:49.233 --> 00:10:52.316
The third thing He said was: "Whatever I

00:10:52.396 --> 00:10:57.790
receive in My Puja, a sixteenth part of it already goes to you first."

00:10:57.870 --> 00:11:02.879
In this way, after granting many boons, the Virata, Shri Krishna,

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:06.589
gave Him permission to take incarnation in this world.

00:11:06.669 --> 00:11:11.106
When Jesus Christ speaks of his father, He is speaking of Krishna,

00:11:11.186 --> 00:11:13.135
He is speaking of the Virata.

00:11:13.215 --> 00:11:16.509
He always spoke of his father, because his father

00:11:16.589 --> 00:11:20.018
had not incarnated together with him in this world.

00:11:20.098 --> 00:11:21.845
His mother was, in person,

00:11:21.925 --> 00:11:24.480
the Adi Shakti of Mahalakshmi Herself.

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:27.249
It is She whom He called the Holy Ghost.

00:11:27.329 --> 00:11:32.236
But at that time He did not speak of the Holy Ghost, and for this reason:

00:11:32.316 --> 00:11:34.943
He did not reveal His mother to the world

00:11:35.023 --> 00:11:38.738
as the Holy Ghost or as any Goddess. Because if the wicked

00:11:38.818 --> 00:11:41.637
rakshasas of that time had come to know that

00:11:41.717 --> 00:11:46.779
she is the Holy Ghost, they would have gone after her. And had such a situation

00:11:46.859 --> 00:11:52.048
arisen, then Jesus Christ Himself would have become so enraged that He would have

00:11:52.128 --> 00:11:55.908
taken up all the powers of destruction that He has and laid

00:11:55.988 --> 00:11:58.614
everything utterly to waste. Jesus Christ

00:11:58.694 --> 00:12:02.282
has eleven Rudras, meaning eleven powers of destruction.

00:12:02.362 --> 00:12:06.206
They are the eleven destructive powers upon our forehead.

00:12:06.286 --> 00:12:08.511
These eleven destructive powers —

00:12:08.591 --> 00:12:11.019
when the Incarnation of Kalki comes,

00:12:11.099 --> 00:12:14.133
about which I am going to tell you tomorrow —

00:12:14.213 --> 00:12:17.180
will then completely carry out whatever work

00:12:17.260 --> 00:12:20.160
of destruction is to be done in this world.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:24.691
These eleven destructive powers of His are seated in our forehead.

00:12:24.771 --> 00:12:27.266
Among them, one power is that of Shri

00:12:27.346 --> 00:12:30.987
Hanumana, and one power is that of Shri Bhairavanatha,

00:12:31.067 --> 00:12:33.773
who are called Gabriel and Michael in the Bible.

00:12:33.853 --> 00:12:35.545
Even if you say it in English,

00:12:35.625 --> 00:12:38.500
you can still awaken that power through the mantra.

00:12:38.580 --> 00:12:41.174
Or whether you say it in Hindi or in Sanskrit,

00:12:41.254 --> 00:12:43.734
that power can still be awakened within you.

00:12:43.814 --> 00:12:48.268
That is to say, on your right side, the Pingala nadi, the Hanumana power flows.

00:12:48.348 --> 00:12:51.900
When your right side is not working and there is trouble in it,

00:12:51.980 --> 00:12:54.348
then one has to take the name of Hanumana.

00:12:54.428 --> 00:12:57.304
At that time, even if you take the name of Gabriel,

00:12:57.384 --> 00:12:59.188
that power still begins to work.

00:12:59.268 --> 00:13:02.255
As for the power on the left side, there the power of

00:13:02.335 --> 00:13:06.111
Saint Michael — or the one whom we call Shri Bhairavanatha — flows.

00:13:06.191 --> 00:13:10.418
If you wish to set the left side working, then you have to take the support

00:13:10.498 --> 00:13:14.218
of Shri Bhairavanatha. Even if you take the name of Saint Michael,

00:13:14.298 --> 00:13:16.383
you can still set this power working.

00:13:16.463 --> 00:13:18.605
Or you can test it through the mantra;

00:13:18.685 --> 00:13:22.687
you can verify for yourself whether what I am saying is correct or not.

00:13:22.767 --> 00:13:25.077
In this way you can understand that those

00:13:25.157 --> 00:13:27.750
who consider themselves Christians, or Hindus,

00:13:27.830 --> 00:13:30.442
or Muslims, and quarrel among themselves

00:13:30.522 --> 00:13:33.984
over worthless matters, are utterly foolish. Because,

00:13:34.064 --> 00:13:36.676
having grown upon one and the same tree,

00:13:36.756 --> 00:13:39.303
all these are relatives of one another.

00:13:39.383 --> 00:13:41.799
Jesus Christ has said that "those who

00:13:41.879 --> 00:13:43.969
are not against me are with me."

00:13:44.049 --> 00:13:49.078
All of this is speaking of those deities who reside upon our various chakras.

00:13:49.158 --> 00:13:52.358
They are all relatives of one another. It is only

00:13:52.438 --> 00:13:55.899
our own relationship that does not connect with them.

00:13:55.979 --> 00:14:01.200
So we cling to each one separately — just as you would pluck a flower off a tree,

00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:03.084
draw out its living essence,

00:14:03.164 --> 00:14:07.482
and then go on fighting among ourselves holding those dead flowers.

00:14:07.562 --> 00:14:09.883
This is the kind of state we are in.

00:14:09.963 --> 00:14:15.119
You will be surprised to know that in Sahaja Yoga the awakening of the Kundalini

00:14:15.199 --> 00:14:17.777
depends very much upon the Agnya chakra.

00:14:17.857 --> 00:14:19.275
Most of the people who

00:14:19.355 --> 00:14:21.933
are moving about in the world these days

00:14:22.013 --> 00:14:25.880
carry a heavy stamp of ego upon them, because, by and large,

00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:30.702
we get caught up in our activities through the ego. It is the ego that pushes

00:14:30.782 --> 00:14:31.982
us into something,

00:14:32.062 --> 00:14:37.050
and it is to feed that very ego that we have gone on doing whatever we have done.

00:14:37.130 --> 00:14:39.904
So if this ego is to be set right, we have to

00:14:39.984 --> 00:14:41.651
remember Lord Jesus Christ.

00:14:41.731 --> 00:14:45.858
When I apply sindoor to each one of you here, you will be surprised

00:14:45.938 --> 00:14:50.434
to know that it is the very chakra of Lord Jesus Christ that I am moving,

00:14:50.514 --> 00:14:52.734
the very chakra that I am awakening.

00:14:52.814 --> 00:14:57.216
This tika that you see on My forehead is the tika of His very blood;

00:14:57.296 --> 00:15:02.733
it is the symbol of it. That is why this red colour carries such great significance.

00:15:02.813 --> 00:15:04.755
In this blood lies that symbol

00:15:04.835 --> 00:15:08.913
which showed that God gave His only begotten Son to this world,

00:15:08.993 --> 00:15:10.935
and you drenched Him in blood.

00:15:11.015 --> 00:15:14.122
It is His sign, so that you may repent, and feel

00:15:14.202 --> 00:15:17.697
sorrow over your foolishness and over your wickedness,

00:15:17.777 --> 00:15:21.143
and reflect upon it: what is this that we have done?

00:15:21.223 --> 00:15:25.639
We think that Shri Mataji has applied sindoor, or that we have applied sindoor,

00:15:25.719 --> 00:15:27.843
so it must be some sign of the Hindus.

00:15:27.923 --> 00:15:30.886
But if you read about John's Revelation in the Bible,

00:15:30.966 --> 00:15:33.425
you will understand, for it is written there

00:15:33.505 --> 00:15:35.965
that this mark will remain upon those people

00:15:36.045 --> 00:15:40.237
when Kalki comes, mounted upon a white horse, carrying these eleven Rudras.

00:15:40.317 --> 00:15:42.665
They did not write down the name of Kalki;

00:15:42.745 --> 00:15:45.316
they said that He will have His very own name,

00:15:45.396 --> 00:15:47.129
and that He alone will know it.

00:15:47.209 --> 00:15:49.948
But when He comes upon the white horse, then they

00:15:50.028 --> 00:15:52.909
will come to know whose mark is upon your forehead.

00:15:52.989 --> 00:15:55.531
By that mark they will recognize who this is.

00:15:55.611 --> 00:15:58.209
There is even a great deal said about Me in it

00:15:58.289 --> 00:16:02.300
— in what manner Sahaja Yoga will come about, and in what manner people

00:16:02.380 --> 00:16:04.583
will receive it, and in what manner the

00:16:04.663 --> 00:16:08.617
Holy Ghost Himself will come and grant these people their realization.

00:16:08.697 --> 00:16:12.142
Because the Incarnation of Jesus Christ took place before us,

00:16:12.222 --> 00:16:15.668
He has spoken about this matter in the most elaborate detail.

00:16:15.748 --> 00:16:18.177
Just as Mohammed Sahib explained, in a very

00:16:18.257 --> 00:16:21.394
elaborate manner, the awakening of the Kundalini

00:16:21.474 --> 00:16:25.526
and the warding off of evil forces and so on, describing their

00:16:25.606 --> 00:16:29.461
workings; in the very same way Jesus Christ explained, in a

00:16:29.541 --> 00:16:32.940
very simple manner, what the weapon of a human being

00:16:33.020 --> 00:16:37.790
is. According to Him, the greatest weapon of a human being is to forgive.

00:16:37.870 --> 00:16:41.203
That which works invisibly in the principle of Shri

00:16:41.283 --> 00:16:46.250
Ganesha, the same thing comes into the human principle and works in the form

00:16:46.330 --> 00:16:50.559
of forgiveness. Forgiveness is in truth a very great weapon, by

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:53.727
which a human being is saved from his own ego.

00:16:53.807 --> 00:16:58.976
Suppose someone has given you great sorrow, or insulted you, or troubled you,

00:16:59.056 --> 00:17:02.547
or caused you harm — then your ego is wounded by it.

00:17:02.627 --> 00:17:07.326
At that moment, if you hold any such feeling in your mind towards him,

00:17:07.406 --> 00:17:09.823
or if you keep thinking in this way,

00:17:09.903 --> 00:17:12.722
that this man did such an injustice to me,

00:17:12.802 --> 00:17:15.756
and you go on dwelling on him day and night,

00:17:15.836 --> 00:17:19.215
then by such useless brooding you will suffer a great deal,

00:17:19.295 --> 00:17:22.617
and the whole time that man will remain active within you.

00:17:22.697 --> 00:17:25.160
Even though he may have forgotten the whole

00:17:25.240 --> 00:17:28.332
thing, and it may have left no effect upon him at all,

00:17:28.412 --> 00:17:31.276
you, by remembering that matter, will go on making

00:17:31.356 --> 00:17:34.907
yourself miserable again and again, and you will go on playing

00:17:34.987 --> 00:17:38.538
into his hands. And when we say, forgive everyone — to forgive

00:17:38.618 --> 00:17:41.539
everyone is the supreme instrument of a human being

00:17:41.619 --> 00:17:45.227
— then what is it that we actually do? This too is a very great

00:17:45.307 --> 00:17:48.334
falsehood, that we forgive — so what is it that we do?

00:17:48.414 --> 00:17:51.274
It is a myth. What do we do? You have told someone,

00:17:51.354 --> 00:17:53.764
"I have forgiven you" — what have you done?

00:17:53.844 --> 00:17:57.545
You have done nothing. You have only saved your own self, from the

00:17:57.625 --> 00:18:00.652
trouble of the other and from brooding upon the other.

00:18:00.732 --> 00:18:03.143
As long as you keep dwelling painfully upon

00:18:03.223 --> 00:18:05.746
that man, you yourself will remain miserable.

00:18:05.826 --> 00:18:10.199
Therefore, forgiveness is for us a very simple and straightforward instrument,

00:18:10.279 --> 00:18:13.362
by which we save ourselves from the torments of others.

00:18:13.442 --> 00:18:16.205
This very great instrument lies within Jesus Christ.

00:18:16.285 --> 00:18:19.261
Jesus Christ possesses those powers — as I have told you

00:18:19.341 --> 00:18:21.413
— within whom the eleven Rudras reside.

00:18:21.493 --> 00:18:23.566
And yet He hung Himself upon the cross,

00:18:23.646 --> 00:18:25.293
He let Himself be hung upon it.

00:18:25.373 --> 00:18:28.933
Why did He hang Himself upon the cross, when He had all the powers?

00:18:29.013 --> 00:18:32.892
He could have slain everyone and could have shattered everyone to pieces.

00:18:32.972 --> 00:18:35.417
And right there, where the Adi Shakti, His own

00:18:35.497 --> 00:18:38.313
Mother, stood weeping beside Him — she could not bear

00:18:38.393 --> 00:18:42.219
it, because, after all, she was in a human birth. She could not bear it,

00:18:42.299 --> 00:18:45.363
that even though all the powers reside within me,

00:18:45.443 --> 00:18:47.695
these people are crucifying my child

00:18:47.775 --> 00:18:52.215
upon the cross, and that today I must stand here to witness this drama.

00:18:52.295 --> 00:18:53.921
The truth of the matter is

00:18:54.001 --> 00:18:55.502
that such people neither

00:18:55.582 --> 00:19:00.272
endure any sorrow, nor become entangled in any pleasure; for them it is all

00:19:00.352 --> 00:19:04.041
a play and a drama. Coming into this world and mounting the

00:19:04.121 --> 00:19:07.248
cross, He showed what great fools these people are

00:19:07.328 --> 00:19:09.392
who crucified Him upon the cross.

00:19:09.472 --> 00:19:12.794
That is why He used to ride upon a donkey, and the

00:19:12.874 --> 00:19:16.594
meaning of this is that His mount was always the donkey.

00:19:16.674 --> 00:19:21.391
The direct corollary of this is that when you have a pain in your head,

00:19:21.471 --> 00:19:25.125
when there is very great trouble, very great suffering,

00:19:25.205 --> 00:19:28.394
then you should say, "I have forgiven everyone."

00:19:28.474 --> 00:19:33.390
Do not take any medicine, do not apply any treatment to it. Only say this,

00:19:33.470 --> 00:19:37.257
that all the people in the world, however many there are,

00:19:37.337 --> 00:19:41.324
who have tormented me or who go on tormenting me to this day —

00:19:41.404 --> 00:19:43.912
I have forgiven them all. You will see,

00:19:43.992 --> 00:19:46.436
your headache will go away. Especially

00:19:46.516 --> 00:19:48.381
for the Sahaja Yogis, who are

00:19:48.461 --> 00:19:50.584
kindled by this Kundalini Shakti,

00:19:50.664 --> 00:19:53.815
the work happens so quickly — because within you,

00:19:53.895 --> 00:19:58.718
Jesus Christ, who is the very embodiment of forgiveness, has been awakened.

00:19:58.798 --> 00:20:04.201
Now see where His place is — it is upon the Agnya chakra. The Agnya chakra within us

00:20:04.281 --> 00:20:05.824
is at the optic chiasma,

00:20:05.904 --> 00:20:09.690
the place where the two nerves of our eyes cross each other;

00:20:09.770 --> 00:20:13.051
and there, in that very centre, is a point. It is so

00:20:13.131 --> 00:20:17.863
subtle even now that the doctors have not been able to see it. But there is

00:20:17.943 --> 00:20:20.404
an extremely subtle door at that place.

00:20:20.484 --> 00:20:23.828
That is why He said, "I am the door." This door is so

00:20:23.908 --> 00:20:28.010
exceedingly subtle that, in order to pass through it from within,

00:20:28.090 --> 00:20:33.138
a personality like Jesus Christ has to come into this world and pass through it.

00:20:33.218 --> 00:20:35.426
Because of our ego, we killed Him —

00:20:35.506 --> 00:20:39.758
because we could not bear that a human being should come as God.

00:20:39.838 --> 00:20:45.087
When some human being says, "I am God," man cannot tolerate it, and that is why

00:20:45.167 --> 00:20:47.692
he killed Him. What wrong had He done?

00:20:47.772 --> 00:20:50.230
He did good to people the world over,

00:20:50.310 --> 00:20:52.835
He taught the whole world good things,

00:20:52.915 --> 00:20:55.772
He taught everyone to live with discipline,

00:20:55.852 --> 00:20:58.975
to live well, to put your life in proper order.

00:20:59.055 --> 00:21:01.181
He kept to the language of love,

00:21:01.261 --> 00:21:04.583
and we gave Him malice and suffering and troubles.

00:21:04.663 --> 00:21:09.234
But those who teach you filthy things and lead you into sinful deeds, and tell you

00:21:09.314 --> 00:21:12.714
to go on doing wicked things — that the more you do them, the

00:21:12.794 --> 00:21:16.083
better you will become — such people who make fools of you,

00:21:16.163 --> 00:21:19.675
we read their books day and night and keep going to their feet.

00:21:19.755 --> 00:21:23.044
You have seen it today — in these times the gurus we follow

00:21:23.124 --> 00:21:26.636
are each more cunning and brazen than the other — are they not?

00:21:26.716 --> 00:21:31.287
For them we squander our money, for them we are ready to do anything in the world.

00:21:31.367 --> 00:21:35.131
And if some such true man comes and stands before us, we crucify him.

00:21:35.211 --> 00:21:38.974
To give such utterly foolish, egotistical people a very great lesson,

00:21:39.054 --> 00:21:40.745
to give them a mighty teaching,

00:21:40.825 --> 00:21:44.534
the Almighty God Himself sent His only begotten son into this world,

00:21:44.614 --> 00:21:46.360
and you nailed Him to the cross.

00:21:46.440 --> 00:21:49.221
Just look at these specimens of your intelligence —

00:21:49.301 --> 00:21:52.629
what marvels you have achieved! And in this very way you have

00:21:52.709 --> 00:21:54.127
done it every single time.

00:21:54.207 --> 00:21:58.516
Whenever any Incarnation came before, man went on doing exactly the same thing,

00:21:58.596 --> 00:22:01.494
and always ran away from the Truth — he kept clinging to

00:22:01.574 --> 00:22:02.971
what merely seemed good and

00:22:03.051 --> 00:22:07.139
kept fleeing from the True. Today I hear that people go to Shirdi a great deal.

00:22:07.219 --> 00:22:09.548
Although Sainath has now departed from there,

00:22:09.628 --> 00:22:11.698
and they have made the place so filthy —

00:22:11.778 --> 00:22:13.693
even so, people keep going to Shirdi.

00:22:13.773 --> 00:22:15.584
They go to Shirdi precisely because

00:22:15.664 --> 00:22:17.424
Sainath is not present here today.

00:22:17.504 --> 00:22:20.609
When the Sainath of Shirdi was alive, He had nothing to eat.

00:22:20.689 --> 00:22:24.156
Today everyone will go to Shirdi. Why? Because now that He is dead,

00:22:24.236 --> 00:22:26.616
all is well. Because now the Sainath of Shirdi

00:22:26.696 --> 00:22:28.404
has become tied around our necks!

00:22:28.484 --> 00:22:31.553
"Our" Sainath of Shirdi — since when did He become yours?

00:22:31.633 --> 00:22:35.563
This is the utter foolishness of man — to run after the one who has died.

00:22:35.643 --> 00:22:37.850
It was for this very foolishness and this

00:22:37.930 --> 00:22:40.407
very ego that Jesus Christ sacrificed Himself.

00:22:40.487 --> 00:22:44.632
And even today man goes on running — leaving aside the one who is before him,

00:22:44.712 --> 00:22:46.004
who is the living proof.

00:22:46.084 --> 00:22:48.723
And he runs after such a one who has died, who is

00:22:48.803 --> 00:22:51.494
finished, and whose place today is somewhere else.

00:22:51.574 --> 00:22:53.836
You have seen that many of the devotees of

00:22:53.916 --> 00:22:56.769
Shirdi who came here were asked to put the question —

00:22:56.849 --> 00:22:58.706
"Shri Mataji, are You Shirdinath?" —

00:22:58.786 --> 00:23:01.571
and the vibrations came within them. It is quite true.

00:23:01.651 --> 00:23:04.075
Whenever any Incarnation came, if you had asked

00:23:04.155 --> 00:23:06.683
the question, you would have received the answer.

00:23:06.763 --> 00:23:09.238
But you went on sitting with the one of the past

00:23:09.318 --> 00:23:11.794
who had died, and you went along leaning on him.

00:23:11.874 --> 00:23:15.639
Because he is not alive today, it suits us well to have him in our hands.

00:23:15.719 --> 00:23:19.536
For instance, I told you the story of Gyaneshwara — that here a very grand

00:23:19.616 --> 00:23:21.525
temple of Gyaneshwara has been built.

00:23:21.605 --> 00:23:23.616
I said, "Let us do contemplation here."

00:23:23.696 --> 00:23:26.172
They said, "No, sir, here you must do the dindi,

00:23:26.252 --> 00:23:28.617
here you must dance." I said, "Did he do that?

00:23:28.697 --> 00:23:32.039
This idol that you have set up here before you — what did he do?"

00:23:32.119 --> 00:23:35.872
Then they began to say, "His case was different; he was someone special."

00:23:35.952 --> 00:23:39.551
I said, "And you — born only for the dindi? He told you to contemplate

00:23:39.631 --> 00:23:41.276
even throughout this whole life,

00:23:41.356 --> 00:23:42.693
he told you to attain God.

00:23:42.773 --> 00:23:45.497
The cause, the root cause of ignorance, is that there

00:23:45.577 --> 00:23:48.354
is no light within you — it is for this that he spoke;

00:23:48.434 --> 00:23:50.130
do that. Why should you do this?"

00:23:50.210 --> 00:23:53.809
"No, no, Mataji, what You say is right, but this cannot be done here."

00:23:53.889 --> 00:23:56.482
I said, "If he were here today, I would speak with

00:23:56.562 --> 00:23:59.208
him — what is there for me to speak with you about?

00:23:59.288 --> 00:24:00.844
What a place I have come into,

00:24:00.924 --> 00:24:05.177
ending up with you." They did not let us contemplate, nor let us teach meditation,

00:24:05.257 --> 00:24:06.969
nor do anything — "only do this."

00:24:07.049 --> 00:24:10.213
So why does a human being cling to what is gone, to the past?

00:24:10.293 --> 00:24:13.353
Because of his ego. Because through it his ego is doubled —

00:24:13.433 --> 00:24:16.545
"Brother, I am the disciple of so-and-so, of such-and-such."

00:24:16.625 --> 00:24:18.855
But if you will not accept the living proof

00:24:18.935 --> 00:24:20.699
that stands right here before you,

00:24:20.779 --> 00:24:24.796
then how is your hunger ever going to be satisfied? What fulfilment is ever

00:24:24.876 --> 00:24:27.286
going to come to you? Just think about this —

00:24:27.366 --> 00:24:29.991
sometimes one should think of one's own interest,

00:24:30.071 --> 00:24:32.106
one should think of one's own welfare.

00:24:32.186 --> 00:24:35.989
The Ganga is flowing here today, and you have gone off to sit somewhere

00:24:36.069 --> 00:24:38.425
where there is no Ganga, to fetch water from

00:24:38.505 --> 00:24:41.023
where the Ganga is not — and you say, "Brother,

00:24:41.103 --> 00:24:42.816
I am sitting in the Ganga." This

00:24:42.896 --> 00:24:44.450
is the kind of talk you make.

00:24:44.530 --> 00:24:47.636
The living proof that stands before you today — accept it.

00:24:47.716 --> 00:24:48.948
The very same situation

00:24:49.028 --> 00:24:51.039
arose in the time of Jesus Christ.

00:24:51.119 --> 00:24:53.781
He made many attempts at Kundalini awakening,

00:24:53.861 --> 00:24:58.535
but they remained so unsuccessful that He cured only twenty-one people in all —

00:24:58.615 --> 00:25:02.460
whereas now, in Sahaja Yoga, thousands of people are being cured.

00:25:02.540 --> 00:25:07.273
He could have cured thousands, but the disciples He had were also great donkeys,

00:25:07.353 --> 00:25:10.192
also good for nothing. Those people only thought

00:25:10.272 --> 00:25:13.052
that Jesus Christ is a man who cures everything

00:25:13.132 --> 00:25:16.741
and does this healing — so, "Come, bring this one to Him too,

00:25:16.821 --> 00:25:21.160
bring that one to Him as well." He said, "Brother, no more than this." When they

00:25:21.240 --> 00:25:25.090
saw Him walking upon the water — because He is the Pranava, the Omkara,

00:25:25.170 --> 00:25:27.394
that is why He could walk upon the water,

00:25:27.474 --> 00:25:29.860
and the Kundalini too is the Omkara itself —

00:25:29.940 --> 00:25:32.326
even when they saw Him walking on the water,

00:25:32.406 --> 00:25:35.877
these people still did not believe in Him. With great difficulty

00:25:35.957 --> 00:25:40.079
He had gathered together barely twelve fishermen. And what else could He do?

00:25:40.159 --> 00:25:42.654
You hardly find anyone simpler than fishermen.

00:25:42.734 --> 00:25:45.283
Just look at our own group here. In those days,

00:25:45.363 --> 00:25:48.530
twelve fishermen were found only with the greatest difficulty.

00:25:48.610 --> 00:25:52.492
Nowadays, if you tried to explain the Kundalini to fishermen — how on earth!

00:25:52.572 --> 00:25:54.718
So you too can understand what those times

00:25:54.798 --> 00:25:57.046
were like — who was there to speak with Him?

00:25:57.126 --> 00:25:59.016
Nowadays people have become extremely

00:25:59.096 --> 00:26:02.007
intelligent; in those days they were of a very low order.

00:26:02.087 --> 00:26:04.131
Somehow He explained it to them, He told

00:26:04.211 --> 00:26:06.612
them, yet they were not the kind to understand.

00:26:06.692 --> 00:26:10.063
All they wanted was, "You set this one right, set that one right."

00:26:10.143 --> 00:26:13.157
Just as it happens in our Sahaja Yoga too — the moment some

00:26:13.237 --> 00:26:16.352
person is given realization, at once he will say, "Mother,

00:26:16.432 --> 00:26:20.568
look, I have a sister, her husband has got such-and-such, will You cure him?"

00:26:20.648 --> 00:26:22.851
Then he comes back having taken a list of

00:26:22.931 --> 00:26:25.025
every sick person in the whole village.

00:26:25.105 --> 00:26:27.522
Why? Because now they have become our agents.

00:26:27.602 --> 00:26:31.577
Now they have taken up the agency. These too are all problems of the ego —

00:26:31.657 --> 00:26:33.591
all of them are problems of the ego.

00:26:33.671 --> 00:26:35.605
A human being should understand that

00:26:35.685 --> 00:26:37.457
the ego is something very subtle.

00:26:37.537 --> 00:26:41.673
Now, the other way is that you fight your own ego. That way too is not right.

00:26:41.753 --> 00:26:44.938
By fighting the ego, you can never get anywhere.

00:26:45.018 --> 00:26:48.468
The ego has to be absorbed within of its own accord.

00:26:48.548 --> 00:26:53.523
When your attention, seated upon the Kundalini, piercing the Brahmarandhra,

00:26:53.603 --> 00:26:55.196
merges into that Virata,

00:26:55.276 --> 00:26:59.721
then the ego becomes a very part of that Virata. The ego that is in

00:26:59.801 --> 00:27:02.455
you people is false. What do you do? Ask

00:27:02.535 --> 00:27:05.321
yourselves — what do you do in this world?

00:27:05.401 --> 00:27:09.117
Why, you take some dead thing and give it another form —

00:27:09.197 --> 00:27:11.585
what great work is this that you do?

00:27:11.665 --> 00:27:15.769
Can you make a fruit out of a flower? First ask the question of yourself.

00:27:15.849 --> 00:27:18.997
This nose, this mouth, this whole beautiful body and all

00:27:19.077 --> 00:27:22.168
else that you have been given — how did you come by it?

00:27:22.248 --> 00:27:25.734
You became a human being from an amoeba — how did that happen?

00:27:25.814 --> 00:27:30.255
With what beauty, without your even being aware of it, you were given all this.

00:27:30.335 --> 00:27:33.595
It is the infinite, boundless grace of God that He created

00:27:33.675 --> 00:27:36.823
you and gave you this human form, this human embodiment.

00:27:36.903 --> 00:27:39.995
Towards Him, what can a human being give but gratitude?

00:27:40.075 --> 00:27:44.398
Towards Him, what indeed can a human being give but reverence? What have you been

00:27:44.478 --> 00:27:47.521
doing till this day? What living work have you ever done?

00:27:47.601 --> 00:27:50.857
Take a test-tube baby — taking a living thing from somewhere,

00:27:50.937 --> 00:27:52.751
somehow nurturing and rearing that

00:27:52.831 --> 00:27:54.326
living thing and bringing it

00:27:54.406 --> 00:27:58.462
up — and over that the human being has become so full of ego! And that too —

00:27:58.542 --> 00:28:02.332
he who did not bring the living quality into being in the first place —

00:28:02.412 --> 00:28:05.027
he merely took the living quality from somewhere,

00:28:05.107 --> 00:28:09.164
just as we do a crossing, and crossed it in that way. How much ego the human

00:28:09.244 --> 00:28:11.387
being has acquired! He reached the moon,

00:28:11.467 --> 00:28:14.841
and how much ego he acquired! Before the One who made thousands

00:28:14.921 --> 00:28:17.278
of universes like this moon and this sun and

00:28:17.358 --> 00:28:20.036
set them in their places, what is your ego anyway?

00:28:20.116 --> 00:28:22.205
Your ego is false, but His ego is true.

00:28:22.285 --> 00:28:24.428
That great Ego — "Aham karoti," meaning,

00:28:24.508 --> 00:28:26.597
He exists, and it is He alone who does.

00:28:26.677 --> 00:28:29.891
This is something I sometimes say in jest — that some people

00:28:29.971 --> 00:28:31.953
travelling in an aeroplane took their

00:28:32.033 --> 00:28:33.747
luggage up onto their own heads.

00:28:33.827 --> 00:28:37.255
People asked them, "Why have you put the luggage on your heads?"

00:28:37.335 --> 00:28:41.688
And they said, "We are lightening the load of this aeroplane a little."

00:28:41.768 --> 00:28:43.423
Your ego is just like that.

00:28:43.503 --> 00:28:45.098
The ego you have is false.

00:28:45.178 --> 00:28:46.526
You do nothing at all.

00:28:46.606 --> 00:28:49.120
To this day you have done nothing at all.

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:51.653
Whatever you have done is all distorted.

00:28:51.733 --> 00:28:55.473
Let Him do it who is the One to do it and who really does it.

00:28:55.553 --> 00:28:58.312
You are only the instrument within His hands.

00:28:58.392 --> 00:29:00.967
Just as this instrument stands here before

00:29:01.047 --> 00:29:03.622
Me today — it does nothing, this you know.

00:29:03.702 --> 00:29:06.338
It is I who am speaking, I am speaking, and

00:29:06.418 --> 00:29:09.082
this one only stands in between as a witness.

00:29:09.162 --> 00:29:11.471
He is being drawn along by this energy.

00:29:11.551 --> 00:29:15.813
In the very same way, you too are an instrument of God. He has made you.

00:29:15.893 --> 00:29:20.333
Let His power flow through you, and put your meaning, your purpose, to use.

00:29:20.413 --> 00:29:23.432
And therefore, to put this meaning to use, upon the

00:29:23.512 --> 00:29:27.893
Agnya chakra — which is the most difficult chakra, the subtlest principle,

00:29:27.973 --> 00:29:30.104
that of the Omkara, of the Pranava —

00:29:30.184 --> 00:29:33.144
that very One descended in person into this world,

00:29:33.224 --> 00:29:36.125
and that very One in person is Shri Jesus Christ.

00:29:36.205 --> 00:29:38.974
Now the Kundalini has a relationship with

00:29:39.054 --> 00:29:42.094
this just as the moon has with its moonlight,

00:29:42.174 --> 00:29:44.133
or the sun with its sun-rays.

00:29:44.213 --> 00:29:49.616
The Kundalini, by her own power — Gauri, by her own power, created Shri Ganesha.

00:29:49.696 --> 00:29:52.331
By her own strength of mind, by her own

00:29:52.411 --> 00:29:55.991
penance, by her own merit, she made Him into Ganesha.

00:29:56.071 --> 00:30:00.596
When Ganesha had come to the stage where He could take incarnation,

00:30:00.676 --> 00:30:02.500
then Jesus Christ was born.

00:30:02.580 --> 00:30:05.552
Now the people in England raise a great deal

00:30:05.632 --> 00:30:08.524
of argument about how He could have been born

00:30:08.604 --> 00:30:11.688
in this way — what they call divine conception —

00:30:11.768 --> 00:30:13.824
how can this be possible? I say,

00:30:13.904 --> 00:30:16.732
how little do these human beings understand,

00:30:16.812 --> 00:30:19.639
how little of all this do they really grasp!

00:30:19.719 --> 00:30:24.217
Do they ever even stop to think how a sprout breaks forth from a seed?

00:30:24.297 --> 00:30:27.060
How do you breathe? How does your movement,

00:30:27.140 --> 00:30:30.546
your functioning take place? Where does the energy in

00:30:30.626 --> 00:30:34.931
your brain come from? In what manner have you come into this world?

00:30:35.011 --> 00:30:37.437
Have you ever diagnosed any of this?

00:30:37.517 --> 00:30:39.540
You say that within the earth,

00:30:39.620 --> 00:30:41.507
in the depths of the ground,

00:30:41.587 --> 00:30:43.609
there is the force of gravity.

00:30:43.689 --> 00:30:47.463
But just consider for a moment — where did it come from?

00:30:47.543 --> 00:30:52.396
Just as little children might suddenly imagine themselves to be Shivaji,

00:30:52.476 --> 00:30:57.397
in the same way these notions of human beings seem to me rather childish.

00:30:57.477 --> 00:31:02.397
This power that seems to you to be active and working within yourselves —

00:31:02.477 --> 00:31:04.828
all this is maya, all this is illusion.

00:31:04.908 --> 00:31:06.897
You have not yet known the Truth;

00:31:06.977 --> 00:31:09.690
you will have to break through this illusion.

00:31:09.770 --> 00:31:12.664
Until this illusion of yours is broken, you will

00:31:12.744 --> 00:31:15.637
go on accepting this very illusion as the Truth.

00:31:15.717 --> 00:31:18.791
And this is the great illusion within you — that it

00:31:18.871 --> 00:31:22.006
is you yourselves who are carrying out all the work.

00:31:22.086 --> 00:31:27.029
And to break this illusion, it was necessary to bring a human form into the world.

00:31:27.109 --> 00:31:29.822
For whenever, in this world, a human being or

00:31:29.902 --> 00:31:34.130
any other living creature has tried to take a step towards evolution,

00:31:34.210 --> 00:31:37.887
at that very time the Incarnations have come into the world.

00:31:37.967 --> 00:31:41.889
You yourselves know that Vishnu took His Incarnation, and coming

00:31:41.969 --> 00:31:43.808
into the world as Shri Rama He

00:31:43.888 --> 00:31:45.787
wandered from forest to forest,

00:31:45.867 --> 00:31:50.402
and to make you understand, to bring a new dimension into your awareness —

00:31:50.482 --> 00:31:54.527
to show what an ideal king is like — He staged such a great drama.

00:31:54.607 --> 00:31:58.590
In the same way was the life of Shri Krishna, and in the same way

00:31:58.670 --> 00:32:00.557
is the life of Jesus Christ.

00:32:00.637 --> 00:32:03.535
But throughout the whole of their lives, if

00:32:03.615 --> 00:32:06.513
you look closely, only one thing stands out

00:32:06.593 --> 00:32:10.030
— and that is your foolishness, your supreme folly.

00:32:10.110 --> 00:32:12.401
Because of which you sent so great

00:32:12.481 --> 00:32:14.166
a principle to the cross.

00:32:14.246 --> 00:32:17.952
That is, the foolishness was exposed to such an extent,

00:32:18.032 --> 00:32:21.537
so tremendous was the folly that came to light, that

00:32:21.617 --> 00:32:25.189
at that time it was even said that if, in His place —

00:32:25.269 --> 00:32:28.436
if there is a thief, let the thief be crucified

00:32:28.516 --> 00:32:32.185
instead — that either the thief should be released or He.

00:32:32.265 --> 00:32:37.544
So these Jews, who today consider themselves to be so very clever, they said, "No,

00:32:37.624 --> 00:32:39.684
give Jesus Christ to the cross."

00:32:39.764 --> 00:32:42.790
Today you know what the condition of these Jews

00:32:42.870 --> 00:32:45.960
is, in what wretchedness they have been trapped.

00:32:46.040 --> 00:32:48.551
So great a sin have they committed from

00:32:48.631 --> 00:32:51.528
time immemorial — can it ever be washed away?

00:32:51.608 --> 00:32:56.565
Even now people remain caught in that very ego, caught in that very same ego,

00:32:56.645 --> 00:33:01.369
and even now they still think that the sinful deeds and the things they have done

00:33:01.449 --> 00:33:03.723
were some great act of merit. Even now,

00:33:03.803 --> 00:33:06.253
if they were to ask forgiveness from God —

00:33:06.333 --> 00:33:08.957
saying that we crucified Your very principle,

00:33:09.037 --> 00:33:13.178
we destroyed that great principle which was Yours, O Lord, forgive us —

00:33:13.258 --> 00:33:16.058
even now they could be forgiven. But for a human

00:33:16.138 --> 00:33:20.920
being, to ask for forgiveness is a very difficult thing. He goes on committing one

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.458
wickedness after another.

00:33:22.538 --> 00:33:26.562
Who is there in this world who can say that they welcomed the saints?

00:33:26.642 --> 00:33:29.106
Look at Nanak Sahib — how terribly he was

00:33:29.186 --> 00:33:32.131
tormented; look at Kabir — how he was persecuted.

00:33:32.211 --> 00:33:35.036
No great person of this world has ever departed

00:33:35.116 --> 00:33:37.820
without suffering at the hands of this world,

00:33:37.900 --> 00:33:41.146
and those who inflict that suffering are human beings.

00:33:41.226 --> 00:33:45.673
But now the world has changed, I am telling you. The Satya Yuga has begun.

00:33:45.753 --> 00:33:48.578
You may try and see for yourselves — now no one

00:33:48.658 --> 00:33:51.363
can inflict suffering upon any saint or sage.

00:33:51.443 --> 00:33:55.229
Enough has happened; now that is not going to go on any longer.

00:33:55.309 --> 00:33:57.418
The reason is that Jesus Christ has

00:33:57.498 --> 00:33:59.969
set in motion a very great power into the

00:34:00.049 --> 00:34:03.182
world, so that now any wicked person, any tormentor,

00:34:03.262 --> 00:34:08.324
may be taught a lesson. His Ekadasha Rudras have today become fully armed and ready.

00:34:08.404 --> 00:34:12.803
And whoever tries to torment any saint or sage will be utterly destroyed.

00:34:12.883 --> 00:34:17.945
To try to torment any saint or sage — this is a great sin. This you must understand,

00:34:18.025 --> 00:34:21.159
and from the example of Jesus Christ you must learn,

00:34:21.239 --> 00:34:23.770
so that we do not commit this folly again.

00:34:23.850 --> 00:34:28.257
If we commit this folly, then we will have failed, and we will be finished forever.

00:34:28.337 --> 00:34:30.886
Now, if any man calls himself an Incarnation, he

00:34:30.966 --> 00:34:35.427
should not be accepted as an Incarnation — this is certain. If every single man says

00:34:35.507 --> 00:34:37.950
"I am an Incarnation, I am an Incarnation," he

00:34:38.030 --> 00:34:41.800
must not be believed. In our own scriptures the criteria are laid down;

00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:45.332
looking at those criteria, if that Incarnation is proved genuine,

00:34:45.412 --> 00:34:46.845
then he should be accepted.

00:34:46.925 --> 00:34:50.430
Someone brought me the news that Jesus Christ had been born again.

00:34:50.510 --> 00:34:54.307
I said, "Oh really, where did this happen?" They said, "He is in Rome."

00:34:54.387 --> 00:34:58.664
I said, "I see, and what does he do?" They said, "He says, 'I am Jesus Christ.'"

00:34:58.744 --> 00:35:01.365
So I said, "In that way even a donkey can say so.

00:35:01.445 --> 00:35:04.225
Saying so hardly makes him Jesus Christ." They said,

00:35:04.305 --> 00:35:06.177
"What is the mark of Jesus Christ?"

00:35:06.257 --> 00:35:08.128
I said, "Tell him to walk on water.

00:35:08.208 --> 00:35:10.989
Tell him now to stop the wind, the water, the storm.

00:35:11.069 --> 00:35:13.315
If he can stop them, and if he can walk on

00:35:13.395 --> 00:35:17.352
water, and if he can bring the dead back to life, then he is Jesus Christ.

00:35:17.432 --> 00:35:20.159
If he cannot do this, then he is not Jesus Christ."

00:35:20.239 --> 00:35:23.703
Then they said that this man does not do any such thing at all.

00:35:23.783 --> 00:35:26.092
Later it came to be known that he ran away

00:35:26.172 --> 00:35:28.757
after taking a great deal of money from people.

00:35:28.837 --> 00:35:32.741
The greatest lesson we can learn from the life of Jesus Christ is this:

00:35:32.821 --> 00:35:35.295
that you remain just as you have been placed.

00:35:35.375 --> 00:35:37.684
Jesus Christ never changed His profession.

00:35:37.764 --> 00:35:39.634
He did not go about advertising to

00:35:39.714 --> 00:35:43.123
the world that "I am a renunciate." He even went to a wedding.

00:35:43.203 --> 00:35:46.612
He went to the wedding, and once there He arranged everything.

00:35:46.692 --> 00:35:50.541
Now, regarding that wedding it is written that He made wine from water.

00:35:50.621 --> 00:35:55.012
And human beings have seized upon this point, saying, "Why, the man made liquor!"

00:35:55.092 --> 00:35:58.074
The meaning of "wine" — even today if you go to Israel,

00:35:58.154 --> 00:35:59.618
or in the Hebrew language —

00:35:59.698 --> 00:36:02.083
is the juice of the grape; it is not liquor.

00:36:02.163 --> 00:36:04.928
It was only later that someone's clever mind got to

00:36:05.008 --> 00:36:08.207
work, thinking it should be fermented and made into liquor.

00:36:08.287 --> 00:36:10.618
And regarding this, if you read the life of

00:36:10.698 --> 00:36:13.192
Moses, then Moses has said in very clear words

00:36:13.272 --> 00:36:15.115
that alcohol and strong substances

00:36:15.195 --> 00:36:18.618
of this kind should not be taken by human beings at all.

00:36:18.698 --> 00:36:21.331
The reason is what I told you the other day

00:36:21.411 --> 00:36:23.800
in connection with the Guru principle —

00:36:23.880 --> 00:36:26.452
that Moses is a very great Guru principle.

00:36:26.532 --> 00:36:28.434
All those who have been Gurus —

00:36:28.514 --> 00:36:31.147
because their work is upon the Nabhi chakra

00:36:31.227 --> 00:36:33.251
and they reside around the Nabhi,

00:36:33.331 --> 00:36:37.849
in the place where the Void is they dwell, and because that has its effect

00:36:37.929 --> 00:36:39.129
upon the liver —

00:36:39.209 --> 00:36:43.363
that is why every Guru, whether it be Nanak, or whether it be Kabir,

00:36:43.443 --> 00:36:46.228
or whether it be your Moses, Abraham, or Socrates,

00:36:46.308 --> 00:36:47.811
all of them forbade liquor.

00:36:47.891 --> 00:36:50.954
Because this is their principle. Each one does the work

00:36:51.034 --> 00:36:54.543
that is his to do. The work of the Gurus is to establish you in

00:36:54.623 --> 00:36:57.073
Dharma, and that is why they forbade liquor.

00:36:57.153 --> 00:37:01.553
And those whose work is different — as, for instance, the work of Jesus Christ,

00:37:01.633 --> 00:37:06.088
which was to open your Agnya chakra, to break your ego — that work He performed.

00:37:06.168 --> 00:37:08.730
The work that is mine, I have to do: to awaken

00:37:08.810 --> 00:37:12.541
your Kundalini and to break open your Kundalini into the Sahasrara.

00:37:12.621 --> 00:37:15.565
But because this is the work of integration, of the whole,

00:37:15.645 --> 00:37:17.676
I have to speak about every one of them.

00:37:17.756 --> 00:37:20.040
I have to speak about Jesus Christ, I have to

00:37:20.120 --> 00:37:22.557
speak about Nanak, I have to speak about Janaka,

00:37:22.637 --> 00:37:25.987
and in the same way I have to speak about Rama, Krishna, and so on

00:37:26.067 --> 00:37:29.367
— about all the Incarnations that have ever come into the world —

00:37:29.447 --> 00:37:31.680
and about Shiva and the rest, all the powers

00:37:31.760 --> 00:37:34.349
that are within us; I have to speak about them all.

00:37:34.429 --> 00:37:37.627
Because today is the time of completeness, of wholeness, and so

00:37:37.707 --> 00:37:41.565
it is of this wholeness that we must speak. Yet even in this, you will see —

00:37:41.645 --> 00:37:45.630
and you will be surprised — that Sahaja Yoga is found mostly in the cities;

00:37:45.710 --> 00:37:47.252
in the villages it is not so.

00:37:47.332 --> 00:37:51.795
It is in the cities that it spreads, slowly, little by little. For to find the Truth

00:37:51.875 --> 00:37:54.107
and to receive the Truth is not within the

00:37:54.187 --> 00:37:56.525
power of the human being. This you have seen

00:37:56.605 --> 00:37:58.518
from history itself. And even today,

00:37:58.598 --> 00:38:01.734
where is the human being going to change? He is in the very

00:38:01.814 --> 00:38:05.746
same condition. The only difference is that the human being of today is so

00:38:05.826 --> 00:38:09.652
scattered, so distracted and absent-minded, as he has never been before.

00:38:09.732 --> 00:38:14.837
And this is why it was said that this work would come to pass only in the Kali Yuga.

00:38:14.917 --> 00:38:19.900
In the tale of Nala and Damayanti, once Nala caught Kali, and Kali said, "Brother,

00:38:19.980 --> 00:38:22.228
if you wish to kill me, then kill me;

00:38:22.308 --> 00:38:24.921
but first hear my glory, hear my greatness.

00:38:25.001 --> 00:38:27.553
There is a special power in me — hear it."

00:38:27.633 --> 00:38:30.429
So Nala asked, "What is your greatness, Kali?"

00:38:30.509 --> 00:38:32.879
Kali replied: "My greatness is that the

00:38:32.959 --> 00:38:35.815
great saints and ascetics in the mountain caves

00:38:35.895 --> 00:38:38.994
will attain this realization in very great numbers;

00:38:39.074 --> 00:38:43.260
and all the justice, all the judgement, will take place in the Kali Yuga."

00:38:43.340 --> 00:38:45.716
Sahaja Yoga itself is this last judgement;

00:38:45.796 --> 00:38:49.246
this is what the Bible calls the last judgement of the Truth.

00:38:49.326 --> 00:38:52.098
It is only after coming into Sahaja Yoga that you

00:38:52.178 --> 00:38:55.063
are judged — whether you stand firm upon it or not.

00:38:55.143 --> 00:38:58.536
But one must remain steady upon it, or he will be sold away.

00:38:58.616 --> 00:39:00.936
For even after attaining the Truth, it is

00:39:01.016 --> 00:39:03.787
difficult for the human being to hold fast to it.

00:39:03.867 --> 00:39:07.035
Many people ask me, "Mother, when did we become steady?"

00:39:07.115 --> 00:39:11.646
This is just like asking: you have come out of the water and stepped into the boat.

00:39:11.726 --> 00:39:13.528
Well, when did you become steady?

00:39:13.608 --> 00:39:17.539
When you felt that you had become steady. When you are riding a bicycle,

00:39:17.619 --> 00:39:19.475
at the very beginning you wobble —

00:39:19.555 --> 00:39:23.486
so when did you become steady? When you felt that you had become steady.

00:39:23.566 --> 00:39:27.606
This is for you yourself to judge — whether you have become steady or not.

00:39:27.686 --> 00:39:31.508
And when you become steady, Nirvikalpa becomes established within you.

00:39:31.588 --> 00:39:35.027
Until the moment our Kundalini descends below the Agnya chakra,

00:39:35.107 --> 00:39:38.952
we cannot come into thoughtlessness. That first abode of Samadhi —

00:39:39.032 --> 00:39:42.760
Nirvichara, thoughtless awareness — does not become established.

00:39:42.840 --> 00:39:46.684
As soon as the Kundalini crosses over this Agnya chakra — that is,

00:39:46.764 --> 00:39:49.735
through the door which Shri Jesus Christ opened for

00:39:49.815 --> 00:39:53.368
us, where it is by taking the very name of Shri Jesus Christ,

00:39:53.448 --> 00:39:58.283
by saying His Lord's Prayer, that the Agnya chakra opens — and after it has opened,

00:39:58.363 --> 00:40:00.577
we enter into the realm of thoughtless

00:40:00.657 --> 00:40:03.511
awareness, into what we may call the destination,

00:40:03.591 --> 00:40:07.182
the Kingdom of God, which is the limbic area in our brain,

00:40:07.262 --> 00:40:11.719
in which all these seven chakras and the sub-chakras as well are seated.

00:40:11.799 --> 00:40:14.338
Until the human being reaches that state,

00:40:14.418 --> 00:40:16.523
thoughtless awareness too does not

00:40:16.603 --> 00:40:18.460
become established within him.

00:40:18.540 --> 00:40:22.874
The greatest cause of the Agnya chakra going out of order is the eyes.

00:40:22.954 --> 00:40:26.111
The human being must guard his eyes very carefully.

00:40:26.191 --> 00:40:28.792
The eye is a tremendously important thing.

00:40:28.872 --> 00:40:32.029
The bowing of the forehead — this is why Shri Jesus

00:40:32.109 --> 00:40:34.990
Christ said, "Do not bow your forehead before anyone."

00:40:35.070 --> 00:40:37.897
Because to bow your forehead before just anyone means

00:40:37.977 --> 00:40:42.245
that you do not know before whom you are about to lose all that you have earned;

00:40:42.325 --> 00:40:45.046
you do not know before what thief you may be bowing

00:40:45.126 --> 00:40:47.260
down your forehead. This is why He said,

00:40:47.340 --> 00:40:49.528
"Do not bow your forehead before anyone."

00:40:49.608 --> 00:40:53.822
You know that in Sahaja Yoga too, I always say: since I have given you nothing,

00:40:53.902 --> 00:40:55.343
why do you come to My Feet?

00:40:55.423 --> 00:40:58.410
But here in our Maharashtra especially, there is a great

00:40:58.490 --> 00:41:01.958
malady of seeking darshan. And just try telling people otherwise.

00:41:02.038 --> 00:41:04.139
Once we went to a certain village where

00:41:04.219 --> 00:41:06.643
there were about five or six thousand people.

00:41:06.723 --> 00:41:11.248
So I said, "Baba, if so many people come to the Feet, it will take a very long time.

00:41:11.328 --> 00:41:12.782
So do not come to the Feet,

00:41:12.862 --> 00:41:14.263
do not take this darshan."

00:41:14.343 --> 00:41:15.797
And everyone became sulky —

00:41:15.877 --> 00:41:18.463
"Mataji, why have You become displeased with us?

00:41:18.543 --> 00:41:21.020
Why are You not letting us come to Your Feet?"

00:41:21.100 --> 00:41:23.955
One should bow one's forehead only before that person

00:41:24.035 --> 00:41:27.860
who is the very representative of God Himself. One should not bow one's

00:41:27.940 --> 00:41:31.172
forehead before just any worthless, good-for-nothing person.

00:41:31.252 --> 00:41:34.551
This is a very important matter. The moment you bow your

00:41:34.631 --> 00:41:36.281
forehead in the wrong place,

00:41:36.361 --> 00:41:38.600
your forehead is turned the wrong way.

00:41:38.680 --> 00:41:41.390
And it is for this reason, you know, that most

00:41:41.470 --> 00:41:44.063
people nowadays have a spoiled Agnya chakra.

00:41:44.143 --> 00:41:47.501
If your forehead has not bowed before the great teachers,

00:41:47.581 --> 00:41:50.822
has not bowed before great souls, but instead has bowed

00:41:50.902 --> 00:41:53.259
in a place where there are wrong people,

00:41:53.339 --> 00:41:57.463
where there is some false guru, then the Agnya chakra becomes spoiled.

00:41:57.543 --> 00:42:03.193
Of all the diseases that afflict the eyes, very many of them arise for this reason —

00:42:03.273 --> 00:42:07.511
because we do not look after the principle of our Agnya chakra.

00:42:07.591 --> 00:42:10.954
The main principle of the Agnya chakra is that the

00:42:11.034 --> 00:42:14.397
human being should read only the most pure things.

00:42:14.477 --> 00:42:17.034
Whatever is impure should not be read.

00:42:17.114 --> 00:42:20.073
People say, "What is the harm in it? We went

00:42:20.153 --> 00:42:23.651
there; now we have to talk with all sorts of people,

00:42:23.731 --> 00:42:27.639
our line of work is such" — but then your eyes too will be spoiled.

00:42:27.719 --> 00:42:30.810
Why do you read the very things that spoil your eyes?

00:42:30.890 --> 00:42:34.215
By looking at wrong people too, your eyes become spoiled.

00:42:34.295 --> 00:42:36.045
Yesterday I told you that Shri

00:42:36.125 --> 00:42:37.816
Jesus Christ said one thing —

00:42:37.896 --> 00:42:41.629
He said to you, "Thou shalt not commit adultery, but I tell you,

00:42:41.709 --> 00:42:45.850
thou shalt not have adulterous eyes." He said this with great emphasis:

00:42:45.930 --> 00:42:49.955
that if there is adultery in your eye, then your eyes will grow weak.

00:42:50.035 --> 00:42:53.736
This does not mean that if you wear spectacles you are a wrong person.

00:42:53.816 --> 00:42:58.258
After a certain age one has to wear spectacles anyway; that is simply a law of life.

00:42:58.338 --> 00:43:02.727
But there are very many causes for the eyes being spoiled, and this is one of them.

00:43:02.807 --> 00:43:04.975
Now there are many people whose attention

00:43:05.055 --> 00:43:08.650
is utterly distracted all the time, running about this way and that;

00:43:08.730 --> 00:43:10.793
they cannot keep their eyes steady even

00:43:10.873 --> 00:43:13.464
for a single minute, the whole time the eyes keep

00:43:13.544 --> 00:43:16.452
darting here and there. And they themselves do not even

00:43:16.532 --> 00:43:19.017
realize why they are rolling their eyes about —

00:43:19.097 --> 00:43:21.710
again and again they will look this way and that.

00:43:21.790 --> 00:43:23.976
God alone knows what they are looking at.

00:43:24.056 --> 00:43:27.841
The greatest effect upon the eyes comes from the way in which you work.

00:43:27.921 --> 00:43:30.054
Suppose you over-work, you are extremely

00:43:30.134 --> 00:43:32.480
engrossed in your work, you do it to excess.

00:43:32.560 --> 00:43:36.399
Even though you may be doing good work — not bad work, not impure work —

00:43:36.479 --> 00:43:40.958
though it is not exactly impure and not exactly pure either, it is a kind of neutral

00:43:41.038 --> 00:43:43.011
work that you are doing. But even so,

00:43:43.091 --> 00:43:45.810
if you work a great deal, if you read a great deal,

00:43:45.890 --> 00:43:49.373
if you sew a great deal, if you read aloud and recite a great deal,

00:43:49.453 --> 00:43:51.013
and if you think a great deal,

00:43:51.093 --> 00:43:52.809
then too your eyes become spoilt.

00:43:52.889 --> 00:43:56.424
The reason for this is that when you work to excess, you forget God.

00:43:56.504 --> 00:43:58.896
Your devotion to God, your communion with Him,

00:43:58.976 --> 00:44:00.640
is no longer settled within you.

00:44:00.720 --> 00:44:01.967
You forget Jesus Christ.

00:44:02.047 --> 00:44:04.283
He was not educated; He had not read even a

00:44:04.363 --> 00:44:06.599
single letter, He never went to any school,

00:44:06.679 --> 00:44:09.954
He never went to any college, nor had He ever seen any teacher.

00:44:10.034 --> 00:44:12.737
Yet today universities have been opened in His name,

00:44:12.817 --> 00:44:15.677
great theological colleges have been built in His name,

00:44:15.757 --> 00:44:18.488
and there, by making themselves professors in those

00:44:18.568 --> 00:44:21.727
theological colleges, people have built great big churches.

00:44:21.807 --> 00:44:24.110
And in those very churches all this goes on

00:44:24.190 --> 00:44:26.546
— to my mind, all of them ought to be called

00:44:26.626 --> 00:44:28.928
jokers; to me they seem nothing but jokers.

00:44:29.008 --> 00:44:33.239
Because a man who is a graduate of God is all right, but those who have done no

00:44:33.319 --> 00:44:37.388
such graduation at all, who have received no initiation whatsoever from God,

00:44:37.468 --> 00:44:41.163
set up all their grand pomp and show among themselves and think, "Ah,

00:44:41.243 --> 00:44:44.295
how great we are!" and they walk about so very seriously.

00:44:44.375 --> 00:44:46.701
These are great foolish jokers. When you

00:44:46.781 --> 00:44:51.143
have not yet even received Self-realization, when not even the line of true

00:44:51.223 --> 00:44:53.433
knowledge has yet appeared within you,

00:44:53.513 --> 00:44:56.304
when not even the light has yet come within you,

00:44:56.384 --> 00:44:59.757
then why do you carry on this kind of pretence and humbug?

00:44:59.837 --> 00:45:03.908
You go about putting on airs as though you were some very great saint.

00:45:03.988 --> 00:45:06.023
And there are elections held in it.

00:45:06.103 --> 00:45:09.476
You have just been reading about the election of the Pope.

00:45:09.556 --> 00:45:13.569
When one sees all the pretence and humbug that goes on in this world,

00:45:13.649 --> 00:45:15.519
a human being like me feels: O God,

00:45:15.599 --> 00:45:18.644
will they ever be able to understand Jesus Christ or not?

00:45:18.724 --> 00:45:22.624
First they crucified Him, and now today they are making a mockery of Him,

00:45:22.704 --> 00:45:24.521
they are turning Him into a farce.

00:45:24.601 --> 00:45:26.738
Among us too there are many such men who

00:45:26.818 --> 00:45:29.970
go about posing as Shankaracharyas — among us too there are

00:45:30.050 --> 00:45:32.614
these great big ones. Nowadays I have heard that

00:45:32.694 --> 00:45:34.190
one Shankaracharya is having

00:45:34.270 --> 00:45:37.155
a golden crown made for himself and an enormous golden

00:45:37.235 --> 00:45:38.571
ceremonial umbrella made,

00:45:38.651 --> 00:45:42.551
because he thought that since the Pope has one, we ought to have one too.

00:45:42.631 --> 00:45:45.955
May such an umbrella fall upon his head with such a thud

00:45:46.035 --> 00:45:49.477
that all these Shankaracharyas will be put in their place!

00:45:49.557 --> 00:45:52.169
The original Adi Shankaracharya did not have

00:45:52.249 --> 00:45:55.276
even enough money to cremate his own mother's body,

00:45:55.356 --> 00:46:00.223
and today these Shankaracharyas are piling up their properties, hoarding up money.

00:46:00.303 --> 00:46:03.271
And we, who consider ourselves so very clever, and

00:46:03.351 --> 00:46:06.318
who have been initiated by such a Shankaracharya —

00:46:06.398 --> 00:46:09.841
today we are the ones filling the bellies of these people.

00:46:09.921 --> 00:46:13.072
Tell me, where does Kundalini come into all this?

00:46:13.152 --> 00:46:16.303
The Kundalini is something utterly pure and true.

00:46:16.383 --> 00:46:20.949
It is not humbug or the running of some shop; it is the absolute Truth.

00:46:21.029 --> 00:46:25.788
And you cannot gauge this Truth until you yourself descend into the Truth.

00:46:25.868 --> 00:46:28.376
You cannot measure it from the outside.

00:46:28.456 --> 00:46:33.086
To attain it, you yourself will have to achieve identity with the Truth,

00:46:33.166 --> 00:46:36.510
you will have to bring about oneness with the Truth.

00:46:36.590 --> 00:46:39.420
When you become one with the Truth, then you

00:46:39.500 --> 00:46:42.782
will know that this is the supreme Truth — that you

00:46:42.862 --> 00:46:46.079
are an instrument of that Supreme Father, that God

00:46:46.159 --> 00:46:49.505
Almighty, through whom this energy is going to flow.

00:46:49.585 --> 00:46:52.480
And from within this you are an instrument of

00:46:52.560 --> 00:46:57.257
that energy, of that power, of that power of love, through whom the power

00:46:57.337 --> 00:47:00.233
of love is going to be transmitted throughout

00:47:00.313 --> 00:47:03.337
the whole world. But how great is the sacrifice

00:47:03.417 --> 00:47:07.792
of Jesus Christ in this, by which He opened our Agnya chakra for us!

00:47:07.872 --> 00:47:12.691
If the Agnya chakra is not all right, the Kundalini will simply not rise.

00:47:12.771 --> 00:47:15.544
If a person's Agnya chakra is caught, then

00:47:15.624 --> 00:47:18.595
his Mooladhara is bound to be caught as well,

00:47:18.675 --> 00:47:21.316
and that Kundalini will simply not rise.

00:47:21.396 --> 00:47:26.546
If the Agnya chakra is caught, then that Kundalini will not rise by any means.

00:47:26.626 --> 00:47:32.039
When there is a catch on the Agnya chakra, then for that we apply sindoor upon it,

00:47:32.119 --> 00:47:34.760
we apply kumkum. People ask me, "Mother,

00:47:34.840 --> 00:47:38.827
why do You apply kumkum?" Especially abroad people say, "Why,

00:47:38.907 --> 00:47:41.260
You are turning us all into Hindus."

00:47:41.340 --> 00:47:46.047
I said, I am turning everyone into Christians. This is the very blood of

00:47:46.127 --> 00:47:49.003
Jesus Christ that I am applying to everyone,

00:47:49.083 --> 00:47:53.135
so that you may remember Him, by which your ego may be removed

00:47:53.215 --> 00:47:56.026
and all your afflictions may be taken away.

00:47:56.106 --> 00:47:58.982
It is only when that sindoor is applied that

00:47:59.062 --> 00:48:02.265
the Agnya chakra opens and the Kundalini goes up.

00:48:02.345 --> 00:48:06.574
Such is the connection between the Kundalini and this great Incarnation.

00:48:06.654 --> 00:48:11.352
Because Shri Sakshat Ganesha, who sits at one station guarding His own chastity,

00:48:11.432 --> 00:48:16.130
He Himself comes upon the Agnya chakra and opens its passage and opens the door.

00:48:16.210 --> 00:48:18.207
What should we do for this chakra?

00:48:18.287 --> 00:48:20.813
What should we do to set this chakra right?

00:48:20.893 --> 00:48:23.536
For this there are many ways. As I have said,

00:48:23.616 --> 00:48:27.316
one should improve one's manner of working. For a man who works

00:48:27.396 --> 00:48:31.213
far too much — you know that he develops a disease like diabetes,

00:48:31.293 --> 00:48:33.342
by which the eyes too become very weak.

00:48:33.422 --> 00:48:36.101
One should reform one's manner of working a little.

00:48:36.181 --> 00:48:38.545
Of course one must work, but there is so much

00:48:38.625 --> 00:48:40.411
imbalance in society that one poor

00:48:40.491 --> 00:48:41.909
man works himself to death,

00:48:41.989 --> 00:48:43.985
while another man does no work at all.

00:48:44.065 --> 00:48:46.902
This imbalance cannot be set right by God; it is human

00:48:46.982 --> 00:48:51.080
beings who can set it right — that everyone should work, so that all may share

00:48:51.160 --> 00:48:54.837
the burden of the work. It should not be that one man's eyes give out,

00:48:54.917 --> 00:48:56.440
that he becomes utterly weak,

00:48:56.520 --> 00:48:59.462
that he gets diabetes, that he dies at a very early age,

00:48:59.542 --> 00:49:03.794
that he gets a heart attack, while other men lie about in sheer idleness.

00:49:03.874 --> 00:49:05.796
Therefore this balance of society

00:49:05.876 --> 00:49:07.682
must come into the human being,

00:49:07.762 --> 00:49:10.790
and the human being must understand that through any

00:49:10.870 --> 00:49:14.132
one excess whatsoever, society itself becomes corrupted.

00:49:14.212 --> 00:49:18.289
Therefore it is not fitting that you should remain in any such excess.

00:49:18.369 --> 00:49:21.107
Improving your manner of working means that you

00:49:21.187 --> 00:49:23.924
should also relax your eyes for a little while.

00:49:24.004 --> 00:49:26.509
And for that there are many arrangements in

00:49:26.589 --> 00:49:29.210
Sahaja Yoga — how the eyes are to be relaxed,

00:49:29.290 --> 00:49:33.894
how one bathes one's eyes in light and in the sun. First, of course,

00:49:33.974 --> 00:49:36.615
realization must definitely take place;

00:49:36.695 --> 00:49:40.419
after that, we can learn how we may set our eyes right,

00:49:40.499 --> 00:49:44.494
how we may take the burden off them, how we may relax them.

00:49:44.574 --> 00:49:48.976
There are many such methods by which you can put your eyes right,

00:49:49.056 --> 00:49:53.321
and by which you can also keep your Agnya chakra in good order.

00:49:53.401 --> 00:49:58.886
But the very best thing is that you keep an eye upon your own ego and talk to it.

00:49:58.966 --> 00:50:02.264
Say to it, "Well now, so you have got into your ego?

00:50:02.344 --> 00:50:06.276
Now, Your Majesty, where are you off to? What is on your mind?

00:50:06.356 --> 00:50:08.639
What do you want to do in your ego?"

00:50:08.719 --> 00:50:11.446
In this way go on addressing your own self.

00:50:11.526 --> 00:50:13.999
Look at yourself in the mirror and say,

00:50:14.079 --> 00:50:16.299
"Well, well, how wonderful you are!

00:50:16.379 --> 00:50:18.725
You think yourself a very great man."

00:50:18.805 --> 00:50:22.800
If in this way you converse with your ego, then if there is any

00:50:22.880 --> 00:50:25.417
pressure on the eyes because of the ego,

00:50:25.497 --> 00:50:30.845
that too will be removed. Now the other side, the back side of the Agnya chakra,

00:50:30.925 --> 00:50:36.407
which we may call the hinder part of Jesus Christ, or which is called Mahaganesha.

00:50:36.487 --> 00:50:40.097
For when Shri Ganesha became Mahaganesha, then He came

00:50:40.177 --> 00:50:43.921
as Jesus Christ; and Jesus Christ is in the very centre,

00:50:44.001 --> 00:50:46.274
and around Him these eleven Rudras

00:50:46.354 --> 00:50:47.892
are under His dominion.

00:50:47.972 --> 00:50:50.846
These eleven Rudras of His — among whom are

00:50:50.926 --> 00:50:53.734
Mahaganesha and Shadanana and the others —

00:50:53.814 --> 00:50:56.350
these eleven Rudras are all around Him.

00:50:56.430 --> 00:50:58.705
Now, the moment you close your eyes

00:50:58.785 --> 00:51:03.011
and the Kundalini rises, you cannot see what is happening inside.

00:51:03.091 --> 00:51:05.821
But if you keep your eyes open, then for a

00:51:05.901 --> 00:51:10.452
minute you may feel that your eyes are dilating, and a sudden darkness

00:51:10.532 --> 00:51:13.458
comes before you, because the dilation of the

00:51:13.538 --> 00:51:17.179
pupil has taken place. When your Kundalini rises within,

00:51:17.259 --> 00:51:22.655
a dilatation of the pupil takes place and the pupils relax, and this is the work of

00:51:22.735 --> 00:51:26.316
the parasympathetic. You can observe this even after realization.

00:51:26.396 --> 00:51:29.811
If a person's Kundalini has not yet pierced the Brahmarandhra,

00:51:29.891 --> 00:51:33.472
and you look at his pupils, they appear very large and very dark.

00:51:33.552 --> 00:51:35.921
But once the Kundalini has pierced through,

00:51:36.001 --> 00:51:37.984
a certain shine comes into the eyes.

00:51:38.064 --> 00:51:40.268
Such a person's eyes are always shining.

00:51:40.348 --> 00:51:43.102
Even if he grows old, still his eyes keep shining.

00:51:43.182 --> 00:51:47.038
And in this way you can recognize whether a person is realized or not.

00:51:47.118 --> 00:51:50.644
How do you recognize the eyes of demons? The eyes of demons were

00:51:50.724 --> 00:51:54.670
like a cat's eyes. Whether you have ever seen a cat's eyes or not,

00:51:54.750 --> 00:51:59.652
I do not know. But in a cat's eye, that white part — the retina — keeps shrinking,

00:51:59.732 --> 00:52:04.455
and the pupil in the middle becomes very tiny and suddenly vanishes altogether.

00:52:04.535 --> 00:52:08.361
If a demon allows you to look into his eyes for a little while —

00:52:08.441 --> 00:52:10.892
because these demonic people come so well

00:52:10.972 --> 00:52:13.483
disguised that you cannot recognize them —

00:52:13.563 --> 00:52:15.357
but if you go to many of these

00:52:15.437 --> 00:52:18.904
gurus and look into their eyes, you will see this in them:

00:52:18.984 --> 00:52:20.960
that within a short while their eyes

00:52:21.040 --> 00:52:23.895
suddenly vanish inward. Mostly they avoid your eyes.

00:52:23.975 --> 00:52:26.390
But if your eyes do meet theirs, you can see

00:52:26.470 --> 00:52:28.885
that, just like a cat's, their eyes suddenly

00:52:28.965 --> 00:52:30.228
roll inward in a flash.

00:52:30.308 --> 00:52:33.382
This is the way to recognize them. Because the principle

00:52:33.462 --> 00:52:37.140
of Jesus Christ is not there. Jesus Christ is not awakened in them.

00:52:37.220 --> 00:52:39.031
There, the most loathsome kind of

00:52:39.111 --> 00:52:42.295
thoughts and dark plotting go on. And for this reason they

00:52:42.375 --> 00:52:45.504
are afraid of you. There will be many such people that if

00:52:45.584 --> 00:52:48.713
you touch them they get a short circuit and collapse flat

00:52:48.793 --> 00:52:52.808
to the ground. There are many such evil spirits roaming about in this world

00:52:52.888 --> 00:52:54.280
who call themselves gurus.

00:52:54.360 --> 00:52:56.822
If you go to garland them, they will throw the

00:52:56.902 --> 00:52:59.793
garland back at you; they will not let you touch them;

00:52:59.873 --> 00:53:01.800
they cannot even wear your garland —

00:53:01.880 --> 00:53:03.807
so low is the level of these people,

00:53:03.887 --> 00:53:05.226
they get a short circuit.

00:53:05.306 --> 00:53:09.588
Now, these are deep matters and subtle matters, which you will understand later.

00:53:09.668 --> 00:53:12.185
But what we were just speaking about, regarding

00:53:12.265 --> 00:53:15.048
Jesus Christ, is this: that by contemplating on Him,

00:53:15.128 --> 00:53:18.019
by thinking of Him, our Agnya chakra can be set right.

00:53:18.099 --> 00:53:20.826
But not the kind of contemplation devised by

00:53:20.906 --> 00:53:24.501
those who have built such inauspicious systems around Him.

00:53:24.581 --> 00:53:27.309
If you look around, they depict Jesus Christ

00:53:27.389 --> 00:53:30.240
as thin, frail, sickly — as if, I do not know,

00:53:30.320 --> 00:53:35.031
they had picked up some TB patient from somewhere. Is this any way to make a

00:53:35.111 --> 00:53:40.193
picture of Jesus Christ? In my view, the painter himself must be sickly like this,

00:53:40.273 --> 00:53:43.063
and that is why he makes such pictures of Him

00:53:43.143 --> 00:53:46.242
and hangs them up, looking wretched and miserable.

00:53:46.322 --> 00:53:48.755
He was extremely strong, He was a very

00:53:48.835 --> 00:53:51.973
radiant Personality, and so beautiful to look at,

00:53:52.053 --> 00:53:54.678
and there was such brilliance within Him,

00:53:54.758 --> 00:53:57.384
and He was a very robust, well-built man.

00:53:57.464 --> 00:54:02.266
He was neither very tall nor very short, but a fine man of ordinary height.

00:54:02.346 --> 00:54:06.956
A man who could lift such a huge cross with His own hands and carry it —

00:54:07.036 --> 00:54:11.198
could He be such a frail, sickly man? The kind of pictures people

00:54:11.278 --> 00:54:14.224
make and circulate, whose photographs are sold

00:54:14.304 --> 00:54:17.838
all over the world, and people think — wow, wow, wow!

00:54:17.918 --> 00:54:22.119
What a picture they have made of Jesus Christ! This is an utter

00:54:22.199 --> 00:54:26.199
insult to Him. Only one great artist, by the name of Rubens,

00:54:26.279 --> 00:54:30.413
whose home I myself have visited — there I saw the very famous

00:54:30.493 --> 00:54:33.294
painting of Jesus Christ called the Ascent

00:54:33.374 --> 00:54:38.174
and Descent of Christ — he has brought out this matter very beautifully,

00:54:38.254 --> 00:54:41.321
and has portrayed Jesus Christ as an extremely

00:54:41.401 --> 00:54:43.335
robust and very joyful being.

00:54:43.415 --> 00:54:45.380
Because nowadays, all over the world,

00:54:45.460 --> 00:54:47.585
only the bony type — tall, broad-framed,

00:54:47.665 --> 00:54:50.906
very lanky girls — are considered beautiful. Absolutely bony!

00:54:50.986 --> 00:54:52.845
If small children were to see them,

00:54:52.925 --> 00:54:55.209
they would feel like vomiting at the sight.

00:54:55.289 --> 00:54:57.361
On top of that she comes wearing heels,

00:54:57.441 --> 00:55:00.362
and she gets the first prize in beauty. Extremely tall,

00:55:00.442 --> 00:55:02.939
utterly thin and frail, as though she will fall

00:55:03.019 --> 00:55:06.419
down or die any moment — and even so she comes walking on heels.

00:55:06.499 --> 00:55:09.527
If little children saw her they would say — good heavens!

00:55:09.607 --> 00:55:11.891
Who dragged this thing from a spider's web?

00:55:11.971 --> 00:55:14.625
But the modern ideas of today have become so

00:55:14.705 --> 00:55:17.238
perverted that we have a taste for looking

00:55:17.318 --> 00:55:18.645
at such spider's webs.

00:55:18.725 --> 00:55:21.741
Because we ourselves are caught in a spider's web,

00:55:21.821 --> 00:55:23.690
the spider's webs appeal to us.

00:55:23.770 --> 00:55:28.113
What was beauty like in the earlier days — when Leonardo da Vinci lived,

00:55:28.193 --> 00:55:30.907
whose painting the whole world reveres today.

00:55:30.987 --> 00:55:33.339
Look at the painting of the Mona Lisa —

00:55:33.419 --> 00:55:35.048
a robust, well-built woman.

00:55:35.128 --> 00:55:40.134
There is the utmost grace within her, and the atmosphere about her is utterly pure.

00:55:40.214 --> 00:55:42.394
And the whole world will come to see her,

00:55:42.474 --> 00:55:46.355
yet when they give the first prize, it goes to these six-foot-seven women

00:55:46.435 --> 00:55:49.891
who come walking there wearing such high heels, sickly and frail,

00:55:49.971 --> 00:55:52.789
looking as if they died yesterday or will die today —

00:55:52.869 --> 00:55:55.953
this is their condition, and people regard this as beauty.

00:55:56.033 --> 00:56:00.127
The very imagination of man has been distorted along with his own perversion.

00:56:00.207 --> 00:56:02.971
And once we have accepted such people as our ideals,

00:56:03.051 --> 00:56:06.082
then day and night women are busy with this one pursuit —

00:56:06.162 --> 00:56:10.014
how can we too take on this spider-web, skeletal condition? And

00:56:10.094 --> 00:56:14.008
for that they will toil, and run about, and do all these things.

00:56:14.088 --> 00:56:16.779
In reality, such women are a great headache.

00:56:16.859 --> 00:56:20.711
The man into whose lap one of them falls comes to know it well.

00:56:20.791 --> 00:56:24.276
There is no sweetness in them, no tenderness of any kind,

00:56:24.356 --> 00:56:26.436
no capacity to bear with anything,

00:56:26.516 --> 00:56:29.023
nor can they give love to their children.

00:56:29.103 --> 00:56:31.488
But such perverted ideas enter into us,

00:56:31.568 --> 00:56:35.848
and by constantly looking at such women, the sense of beauty within us

00:56:35.928 --> 00:56:37.410
becomes so utterly corrupted.

00:56:37.490 --> 00:56:41.321
Now it may seem to you that Mataji is talking of very old, outdated things,

00:56:41.401 --> 00:56:43.751
but what I am telling you are eternal truths —

00:56:43.831 --> 00:56:46.897
that you cast an impure glance upon every woman on the road.

00:56:46.977 --> 00:56:48.254
Even upon a single woman,

00:56:48.334 --> 00:56:51.502
this is a great sin. So think how many sinful deeds you commit

00:56:51.582 --> 00:56:54.596
day and night walking along the street. I am telling you in

00:56:54.676 --> 00:56:57.179
the relationship of a Mother that you should give

00:56:57.259 --> 00:56:59.609
up all these pursuits. These are all worthless

00:56:59.689 --> 00:57:02.448
things. There is no gain whatsoever in doing all this.

00:57:02.528 --> 00:57:04.776
Jesus Christ told it two thousand years ago,

00:57:04.856 --> 00:57:06.735
but today I am saying that the poor

00:57:06.815 --> 00:57:09.660
One could not explain it so openly. Whatever He said,

00:57:09.740 --> 00:57:13.660
He said with great force. But you took Him up and put Him upon the cross.

00:57:13.740 --> 00:57:17.873
For one thing, you cannot crucify me — that is the first point; and secondly,

00:57:17.953 --> 00:57:20.477
I am clever enough that I will tell you in such

00:57:20.557 --> 00:57:22.973
a way that it will get right into your skull.

00:57:23.053 --> 00:57:26.489
Because He had not explained what happens when you do this deed.

00:57:26.569 --> 00:57:29.360
He only said — do not do this, it is a filthy thing.

00:57:29.440 --> 00:57:32.393
Adulterous eyes are very, very much against your being.

00:57:32.473 --> 00:57:35.859
But He did not say what happens by keeping adulterous eyes,

00:57:35.939 --> 00:57:37.719
what its evil consequences are.

00:57:37.799 --> 00:57:41.013
Day and night this very thought runs about in our minds.

00:57:41.093 --> 00:57:44.077
And by doing this, what will you save yourself from?

00:57:44.157 --> 00:57:45.822
Are you a human being at all?

00:57:45.902 --> 00:57:49.633
You will become worse than an animal, worse even than the beasts.

00:57:49.713 --> 00:57:52.927
That is why in our Yoga Shastra it is said that one must

00:57:53.007 --> 00:57:56.106
restrain the tendencies of one's attention — check it,

00:57:56.186 --> 00:57:59.802
check it, keep it upon the right path. One should keep it bowed

00:57:59.882 --> 00:58:03.579
in humility before God, and one should walk in that direction.

00:58:03.659 --> 00:58:06.581
We are built upon Yoga; ours is the land of Yoga.

00:58:06.661 --> 00:58:10.597
We are not egoists, nor are we meant to be. Those who wish to make

00:58:10.677 --> 00:58:13.360
themselves egoists may take their immigration

00:58:13.440 --> 00:58:16.660
and go off to England. They have no need to live here,

00:58:16.740 --> 00:58:19.185
and no need to spoil this country either.

00:58:19.265 --> 00:58:21.173
We are not to indulge in egoism.

00:58:21.253 --> 00:58:24.473
We are to live here in the manner of the Land of Yoga.

00:58:24.553 --> 00:58:25.984
And a day will come when

00:58:26.064 --> 00:58:27.555
we shall attain our Yoga,

00:58:27.635 --> 00:58:30.278
and when we receive the fruit of our holy

00:58:30.358 --> 00:58:35.580
land, then the whole world will be at your feet. On that day they will know where

00:58:35.660 --> 00:58:38.819
Jesus Christ truly belonged, and on that day they

00:58:38.899 --> 00:58:43.347
will know where Jesus Christ has actually been received and honoured.

00:58:43.427 --> 00:58:46.651
Even today, in our land of India, woman is held in

00:58:46.731 --> 00:58:50.212
great respect; the womankind is held in great respect.

00:58:50.292 --> 00:58:52.742
Even today the mother is regarded as a

00:58:52.822 --> 00:58:55.787
mother and the sister is regarded as a sister.

00:58:55.867 --> 00:58:58.996
They will come here and understand that Jesus Christ

00:58:59.076 --> 00:59:02.144
is most honoured and most followed in this country,

00:59:02.224 --> 00:59:06.917
and not in those countries that go about calling themselves Christian Nations.

00:59:06.997 --> 00:59:11.028
Whatever has to be told to you is so very much that — as you know —

00:59:11.108 --> 00:59:14.899
I have said that a book of five hundred pages has been written,

00:59:14.979 --> 00:59:19.130
and in it this boy sent I do not know how many pages on Jesus Christ.

00:59:19.210 --> 00:59:24.264
Because he was a Catholic by community, he has given a good deal of thought to that.

00:59:24.344 --> 00:59:28.429
And he himself had earlier gone off somewhere to become a priest.

00:59:28.509 --> 00:59:32.845
And in this way he made a great investigation into all these matters.

00:59:32.925 --> 00:59:35.878
And when he understood that Jesus Christ dwells

00:59:35.958 --> 00:59:38.786
within our very own selves and is within us —

00:59:38.866 --> 00:59:43.893
And until we are reborn... Jesus Christ has said that you have to be born again.

00:59:43.973 --> 00:59:47.932
This second birth comes only through the path of the Kundalini.

00:59:48.012 --> 00:59:51.908
And until the Kundalini is awakened, you cannot be born again.

00:59:51.988 --> 00:59:56.799
Until your second birth takes place, you will not know God. Read the Bible afresh —

00:59:56.879 --> 00:59:59.488
read it after you have got your realization —

00:59:59.568 --> 01:00:01.886
and you will be amazed that in all of it

01:00:01.966 --> 01:00:05.676
Jesus Christ has done nothing but sing the glory of Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:05.756 --> 01:00:09.234
Each and every word of His is such that we take it to heart.

01:00:09.314 --> 01:00:12.097
But those who have no eyes cannot understand it.

01:00:12.177 --> 01:00:15.249
They even mock at it and speak false things about it.

01:00:15.329 --> 01:00:17.937
Now here He said a profound thing — that I am

01:00:18.017 --> 01:00:20.568
the path, I am the door, that I am the door,

01:00:20.648 --> 01:00:23.195
I am the path. The meaning of this is that He

01:00:23.275 --> 01:00:25.821
is the path and He is the door — quite right,

01:00:25.901 --> 01:00:27.995
for the path passes through the door.

01:00:28.075 --> 01:00:32.603
Now the meaning given to it became that He is the only one — they clung to that,

01:00:32.683 --> 01:00:36.588
that after Him there can be no one else. And who are these people who

01:00:36.668 --> 01:00:39.893
depend on that idea? These people who have set themselves

01:00:39.973 --> 01:00:41.898
up as clowns posing as Christians.

01:00:41.978 --> 01:00:44.354
Any man comes along and gives you baptism.

01:00:44.434 --> 01:00:45.906
To give baptism is in fact

01:00:45.986 --> 01:00:47.627
to break open your Sahasrara.

01:00:47.707 --> 01:00:51.035
To break open the Sahasrara and to draw the Kundalini out

01:00:51.115 --> 01:00:54.442
through it and grant realization — that alone is baptism.

01:00:54.522 --> 01:00:58.200
That is to say, the very final act of the Kundalini is baptism.

01:00:58.280 --> 01:01:01.782
And these people who keep giving you baptism in the church —

01:01:01.862 --> 01:01:04.431
what authority do they have to give baptism?

01:01:04.511 --> 01:01:08.306
They are merely attempting something to which they have no right.

01:01:08.386 --> 01:01:11.655
And otherwise, they have now started philanthropic work.

01:01:11.735 --> 01:01:15.938
Philanthropic work — well, come on, brother, serve the poor, serve them.

01:01:16.018 --> 01:01:19.457
Now you will say — Mataji, but this is a good work.

01:01:19.537 --> 01:01:23.852
It is good, yes, but this is not God's work, this is man's work.

01:01:23.932 --> 01:01:26.899
You made them poor, you made them miserable,

01:01:26.979 --> 01:01:29.272
and now you are to set them right?

01:01:29.352 --> 01:01:34.477
God's work is not to go and serve the poor, and first to manufacture poverty

01:01:34.557 --> 01:01:36.377
and then to serve the poor.

01:01:36.457 --> 01:01:39.829
God's work is to take you into the Kingdom of God,

01:01:39.909 --> 01:01:42.943
to unite you with God; to fill you completely

01:01:43.023 --> 01:01:46.760
with His joy, His grace, His peace, His splendour. That is God's work.

01:01:46.840 --> 01:01:50.736
It is not that a man steals, cheats, tells lies, and roams about all over

01:01:50.816 --> 01:01:54.553
the world crying 'I am poor, I am poor,' and you go and kiss his feet.

01:01:54.633 --> 01:01:57.408
This philanthropic work is the work of human beings,

01:01:57.488 --> 01:02:00.104
and we must understand this fully and completely.

01:02:00.184 --> 01:02:04.241
I asked, "Tell me, are these Christian people doing any philanthropic work?"

01:02:04.321 --> 01:02:07.577
Wherever they went, they went only to make people Christians.

01:02:07.657 --> 01:02:09.579
Wherever tribal people were sitting,

01:02:09.659 --> 01:02:11.954
they reached there to do philanthropic work

01:02:12.034 --> 01:02:14.154
— and they make everyone a Christian.

01:02:14.234 --> 01:02:16.124
Whatever you turn a donkey into —

01:02:16.204 --> 01:02:18.668
make him a Christian or make him a Muslim —

01:02:18.748 --> 01:02:20.925
the donkey will still remain a donkey.

01:02:21.005 --> 01:02:23.010
Just by changing that label on him,

01:02:23.090 --> 01:02:25.840
do you think it is going to make any difference?

01:02:25.920 --> 01:02:29.472
But these fools think that through this their democracy grows.

01:02:29.552 --> 01:02:31.958
These people have turned it into politics.

01:02:32.038 --> 01:02:34.273
Whatever it may be, ask them directly —

01:02:34.353 --> 01:02:35.899
why do you do philanthropy?

01:02:35.979 --> 01:02:40.219
And the quotation from the Bible that they gave in answer is very amusing,

01:02:40.299 --> 01:02:43.653
and when you see it you will realize how foolish those people were.

01:02:43.733 --> 01:02:47.138
They said that Mary Magdalene bought an oil — a very expensive oil —

01:02:47.218 --> 01:02:48.418
and she brought it,

01:02:48.498 --> 01:02:52.549
and she began to say to Jesus Christ that "I wish to anoint Your body with this."

01:02:52.629 --> 01:02:56.531
Then Judas said, "Brother, why are you wasting such expensive oil on His body?

01:02:56.611 --> 01:02:58.572
It could be sold and given to the poor.

01:02:58.652 --> 01:03:00.114
He was the philanthropic one!

01:03:00.194 --> 01:03:03.200
And it was he who, in the end, had Jesus Christ handed over.

01:03:03.280 --> 01:03:05.589
And even those thirty pieces of silver that he

01:03:05.669 --> 01:03:08.177
received, those too he distributed among the poor.

01:03:08.257 --> 01:03:10.456
It is just like the way so many people do

01:03:10.536 --> 01:03:13.111
black marketing — they do black marketing here —

01:03:13.191 --> 01:03:15.176
and then they go and stand before the

01:03:15.256 --> 01:03:17.294
temple and distribute loaves of bread,

01:03:17.374 --> 01:03:19.949
or they go and give money to some sadhu or baba.

01:03:20.029 --> 01:03:22.443
And in this way they console their own soul —

01:03:22.523 --> 01:03:25.098
"Well, brother, we did a little black marketing,

01:03:25.178 --> 01:03:28.343
but at least we have also done a little philanthropic work,

01:03:28.423 --> 01:03:31.051
a little meritorious deed." In the very same way,

01:03:31.131 --> 01:03:32.794
he said that whatever there is,

01:03:32.874 --> 01:03:35.932
give it to the poor people — this is what Mr. Judas said.

01:03:36.012 --> 01:03:40.640
So Jesus Christ at that moment gave this reply: "These poor are for ever,

01:03:40.720 --> 01:03:43.383
but I am for a short time." The meaning is

01:03:43.463 --> 01:03:47.393
that this divine life has come for a short time. Look at that,

01:03:47.473 --> 01:03:49.248
that is what has importance.

01:03:49.328 --> 01:03:52.245
These poor are an everlasting headache anyway.

01:03:52.325 --> 01:03:57.016
And about very rich people too He had said that "It is easy for a camel to

01:03:57.096 --> 01:03:59.188
pass through the eye of a needle,

01:03:59.268 --> 01:04:02.438
but it is an impossibility for a rich man to enter

01:04:02.518 --> 01:04:06.005
into the kingdom of God." These two extremes He pointed

01:04:06.085 --> 01:04:08.975
out throughout His life. You must put an end to

01:04:09.055 --> 01:04:12.129
both of these extremes. And the Christian people —

01:04:12.209 --> 01:04:17.251
they are either at this extreme, or at that extreme. Now this philanthropic work —

01:04:17.331 --> 01:04:19.729
here too many people, after seeing Him,

01:04:19.809 --> 01:04:23.130
set up missions. And the people who come through these

01:04:23.210 --> 01:04:25.177
missions do not get realization.

01:04:25.257 --> 01:04:28.885
They say, "Mother, we do so much mission work." Yes, do it!

01:04:28.965 --> 01:04:31.056
Do it officially, do it privately.

01:04:31.136 --> 01:04:34.702
You may call it a public service, it is good for everyone.

01:04:34.782 --> 01:04:38.442
Yes, there are many names for it too — call it social work.

01:04:38.522 --> 01:04:40.506
But this is not the work of God.

01:04:40.586 --> 01:04:43.191
There is no need for any misappropriation.

01:04:43.271 --> 01:04:45.442
The work of God flows unobstructed.

01:04:45.522 --> 01:04:49.678
Just as people will say, "Mother, You too cure people's illnesses."

01:04:49.758 --> 01:04:53.418
We do not really do anything; they get cured by themselves.

01:04:53.498 --> 01:04:57.529
We awaken the Kundalini. We are not doing any work of that sort —

01:04:57.609 --> 01:05:02.013
that we should go and reach some hospital, take twenty-five sick people

01:05:02.093 --> 01:05:04.777
there and cure them. Because it is this love flowing

01:05:04.857 --> 01:05:07.798
from within us that cures. Jesus Christ too cured people.

01:05:07.878 --> 01:05:10.871
But He did not go and sit there serving at someone's feet.

01:05:10.951 --> 01:05:13.635
Human beings must understand this matter completely.

01:05:13.715 --> 01:05:17.173
The mistakes that these people have made, you should not make them.

01:05:17.253 --> 01:05:20.452
Your work is that you yourself should attain Self-realization.

01:05:20.532 --> 01:05:23.474
After attaining Self-realization, all these powers awaken

01:05:23.554 --> 01:05:26.960
within you by themselves — meaning you can cure someone's illness.

01:05:27.040 --> 01:05:30.962
Among us, many have even cured cancer — it is true! There is no lie in this.

01:05:31.042 --> 01:05:34.815
Cancer can be cured only through Sahaja Yoga, and this too is the truth.

01:05:34.895 --> 01:05:37.724
Now here, the one who put the garland around My neck —

01:05:37.804 --> 01:05:39.795
this lady here cured fifty-odd people.

01:05:39.875 --> 01:05:43.543
I said to her, "Stop! Why do you cure them?" Because while doing this,

01:05:43.623 --> 01:05:46.714
it then came into her mind that these people are of no use.

01:05:46.794 --> 01:05:48.680
After getting cured, they went away.

01:05:48.760 --> 01:05:51.013
They do not seek God. For them it is simply

01:05:51.093 --> 01:05:54.394
that they should use God only so that their illness gets cured.

01:05:54.474 --> 01:05:56.727
They do not have the idea of attaining God.

01:05:56.807 --> 01:06:00.056
Why would God cure such bodies too, that are not lamps of God?

01:06:00.136 --> 01:06:02.891
Do you repair such lamps that are of no use?

01:06:02.971 --> 01:06:06.979
Such lamp-pillars are set up that give light to the whole world.

01:06:07.059 --> 01:06:09.563
God too has intelligence. He is not such

01:06:09.643 --> 01:06:12.524
that He would go about curing fools like this.

01:06:12.604 --> 01:06:17.300
Those human beings who do not have the power to spread the light of God and

01:06:17.380 --> 01:06:19.948
to set right the path of God, and to give

01:06:20.028 --> 01:06:22.845
something in a special way to people for that

01:06:22.925 --> 01:06:25.994
— to such people who do not do this work, no God,

01:06:26.074 --> 01:06:28.954
nothing of this kind, wishes to give anything.

01:06:29.034 --> 01:06:32.019
Those people who keep themselves on such a wrong

01:06:32.099 --> 01:06:35.394
path that "we are doing great big philanthropic work,

01:06:35.474 --> 01:06:38.086
we are doing great service to the country"

01:06:38.166 --> 01:06:41.088
— just now a gentleman telephoned me saying, "I

01:06:41.168 --> 01:06:44.215
had gone there to give relief to people." I said,

01:06:44.295 --> 01:06:49.020
"Keep giving just that; that very thing is good for you." Then someone said,

01:06:49.100 --> 01:06:52.893
"I had gone to cure someone's eyes." Let them keep doing it —

01:06:52.973 --> 01:06:57.077
there is no harm in it. You do it — do it as an official, or do it

01:06:57.157 --> 01:06:59.826
as a human being, do it as a social worker.

01:06:59.906 --> 01:07:02.017
But this is never the work of God.

01:07:02.097 --> 01:07:04.394
You attach every single thing to God.

01:07:04.474 --> 01:07:08.075
I have even seen this — Sainath Bidi! There should be some

01:07:08.155 --> 01:07:12.314
limit to everything. You used to attach every single thing to God —

01:07:12.394 --> 01:07:14.070
Sadhana Soap! Just imagine,

01:07:14.150 --> 01:07:15.516
is there no end to it!

01:07:15.596 --> 01:07:18.203
And Vishnu-brand asafoetida! Lakshmi-brand

01:07:18.283 --> 01:07:19.835
asafoetida! Just imagine!

01:07:19.915 --> 01:07:24.012
Have these people made a mockery of God? And what benefit is going

01:07:24.092 --> 01:07:26.824
to come to you from this? They say, "Mother,

01:07:26.904 --> 01:07:29.662
we do it because it will be auspicious for us." Did

01:07:29.742 --> 01:07:34.176
it become auspicious? — "We will earn more money." You are never going to earn it!

01:07:34.256 --> 01:07:36.203
If you do your business in this way,

01:07:36.283 --> 01:07:37.905
you will face great suffering.

01:07:37.985 --> 01:07:40.310
This is an insult to Shri Lakshmi Herself —

01:07:40.390 --> 01:07:42.391
that they turned Her into asafoetida!

01:07:42.471 --> 01:07:45.175
In the very same way, a human being does many such

01:07:45.255 --> 01:07:47.850
things, all of which amount to misappropriation.

01:07:47.930 --> 01:07:50.039
And in exactly this way, we have played

01:07:50.119 --> 01:07:52.607
this very same game with Jesus Christ as well.

01:07:52.687 --> 01:07:54.904
We should understand that Jesus Christ is

01:07:54.984 --> 01:07:57.667
neither anyone's property nor anyone's possession.

01:07:57.747 --> 01:08:00.000
He came into this world for the redemption

01:08:00.080 --> 01:08:01.797
and welfare of all of humankind;

01:08:01.877 --> 01:08:05.471
He is the Omkara principle of God. And it was this Omkara principle

01:08:05.551 --> 01:08:07.483
that offered itself as a sacrifice —

01:08:07.563 --> 01:08:11.586
only He can offer such a sacrifice, no one else. All the other Incarnations

01:08:11.666 --> 01:08:15.154
who came afterward — their bodies were made of the earth element,

01:08:15.234 --> 01:08:17.165
but His body was made of the Pranava

01:08:17.245 --> 01:08:20.196
principle, and that is why His resurrection took place.

01:08:20.276 --> 01:08:23.227
Now, after the resurrection had happened, all those who

01:08:23.307 --> 01:08:24.809
were His disciples accepted,

01:08:24.889 --> 01:08:26.502
"Yes, indeed, He truly was what

01:08:26.582 --> 01:08:28.091
He said He was," because they

01:08:28.171 --> 01:08:31.345
had seen Him in His bodily form — only then did they believe.

01:08:31.425 --> 01:08:33.350
But then who was to come to give them

01:08:33.430 --> 01:08:37.384
their realization? Then they set about doing all sorts of odd things — doing

01:08:37.464 --> 01:08:40.742
this, doing that, all kinds of things from all over the world —

01:08:40.822 --> 01:08:43.840
and people began to shout and scream in the name of Jesus.

01:08:43.920 --> 01:08:48.186
When they started all this screaming and shouting, evil spirits entered into them.

01:08:48.266 --> 01:08:50.868
And they began to speak in all kinds of languages,

01:08:50.948 --> 01:08:53.289
and they have written this down in the Bible.

01:08:53.369 --> 01:08:57.970
Now everyone thinks that this very entering of a spirit within oneself is itself

01:08:58.050 --> 01:09:00.005
the blessing of the Divine Spirit.
